{"title_page": "Carlos Humberto Reyes", "text_new": "[[File:Carlos H Reyes.jpg|right|thumb|200px|Carlos H. Reyes in July 2009, with [[Flag of Honduras|Honduran flag]] in background]]\n'''Carlos Humberto Reyes''' (often, '''Carlos H. Reyes''') is leader of the [[trade union]] [[Union of Beverage and Related Industry Workers|STIBYS]] in [[Honduras]], a coordinator of the [[National Resistance Front (Honduras)|Frente Nacional de Resistencia contra el Golpe de Estado en Honduras]] and was an independent candidate<ref name=\"official_candidate_order\" /> for the [[2009 Honduran general election#Presidential election|2009 Honduran presidential election]] before pulling out on November 9.<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\" /> He was injured by security forces during demonstrations on 30 July 2009.<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\" /><ref name=\"enlazando_mission090730\" />\n\n==Candidacy in 2009 presidential election==\nCarlos H. Reyes was an [[independent (politics)|independent]] candidate in the [[2009 Honduran general election|2009 presidential election]] in Honduras, which were held on 29 November 2009.<ref name=\"official_candidate_order\">{{cite web |title=Publicaci\u00f3n del voto despeja inc\u00f3gnitas |publisher=Tiempo |year=2009 |url=http://tiempo.hn/secciones/politica/1956-publicacion-del-voto-despeja-incognitas |accessdate=2009-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5irH5p3mA?url=http://tiempo.hn/secciones/politica/1956-publicacion-del-voto-despeja-incognitas |archivedate=2009-08-07 |url-status=dead |language=es }}</ref>\n\nAn international human rights mission including, among others, [[:es:Nora Morales de Corti\u00f1as|Nora Corti\u00f1as]] of [[Mothers of the Plaza de Mayo]], reported that Carlos Humberto Reyes was injured on 30 July 2009 when \"the army and the special forces of the National Police of Honduras attacked thousands of pacific demonstrators, with fire weapons, wood and rubber projectiles and as well as tear gas, thrown even from helicopters.\"<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\">{{cite web |title=Defying threats, Zelaya supporters continue protests |work=[[La Prensa (Texas)|La Prensa]] |date=2009-07-31 |url=http://www.laprensasa.com/2.0/3/309/273599/America-in-English/Defying-threats-Zelaya-supporters-continue-protests.html |accessdate=2009-08-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713183835/http://www.laprensasa.com/2.0/3/309/273599/America-in-English/Defying-threats-Zelaya-supporters-continue-protests.html |archivedate=2011-07-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"enlazando_mission090730\">{{cite web|title=International Mission denounces the brutal repression of pacific demonstrations|publisher=Agencia Latinoamerica de Informaci\u00f3n|date=2009-07-30|url=http://www.alainet.org/active/32099|accessdate=2009-08-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724231655/http://www.alainet.org/active/32099|archivedate=2011-07-24|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 November 2009, following a national meeting of leaders of the [[National Resistance Front (Honduras)|National Resistance Front against the coup d'\u00e9tat]], Reyes declared the withdrawal of his candidacy, on the grounds of not legitimising the coup d'\u00e9tat and fraudulent elections.<ref name=\"tiempo_reyes_withdraws\">{{cite news |language=Spanish |title=Carlos H. Reyes anuncia su retiro de los comicios |date=2009-11-08 |publisher=[[El Tiempo (Honduras)]] |url=http://www.tiempo.hn/secciones/crisis-politica/7119-carlos-h-reyes-anuncia-su-retiro-de-los-comicios |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091112061320/http://www.tiempo.hn/secciones/crisis-politica/7119-carlos-h-reyes-anuncia-su-retiro-de-los-comicios |archivedate=2009-11-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"tribuna_reyes_withdraws\">{{cite news |language=Spanish |title=Carlos H. Reyes oficializa su renuncia |date=2009-11-09 |publisher=[[La Tribuna (Honduras)]] |url=http://www.latribuna.hn/web2.0/?p=61658 |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030130239/http://www.latribuna.hn/web2.0/?p=61658 |archivedate=2010-10-30 |url-status=dead }}</ref> The Honduran newspapers ''El Tiempo'' and ''La Tribuna'' showed Reyes' right hand in a plaster cast.<ref name=\"tiempo_reyes_withdraws\" /><ref name=\"tribuna_reyes_withdraws\" />\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Carlos Reyes}}\n*[http://www.facebook.com/pages/Carlos-H-Reyes/185768405450?v=feed&story_fbid=236702365450&ref=mf Reyes' ] [[facebook]] entry\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Reyes, Carlos Humberto}}\n[[Category:Candidates for President of Honduras]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Honduran trade unionists]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{Honduras-politician-stub}}\n{{Trade-unionist-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "[[File:Carlos H Reyes.jpg|right|thumb|200px|Carlos H. Reyes in July 2009, with [[Flag of Honduras|Honduran flag]] in background]]\n'''Carlos Humberto Reyes''' (often, '''Carlos H. Reyes''') is leader of the [[trade union]] [[Union of Beverage and Related Industry Workers|STIBYS]] in [[Honduras]], a coordinator of the [[National Resistance Front (Honduras)|Frente Nacional de Resistencia contra el Golpe de Estado en Honduras]] and was an independent candidate<ref name=\"official_candidate_order\" /> for the [[2009 Honduran general election#Presidential election|2009 Honduran presidential election]] before pulling out on November 9.<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\" /> He was injured by security forces during demonstrations on 30 July 2009.<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\" /><ref name=\"enlazando_mission090730\" />\n\n==Candidacy in 2009 presidential election==\nCarlos H. Reyes was an [[independent (politics)|independent]] candidate in the [[2009 Honduran general election|2009 presidential election]] in Honduras, which were held on 29 November 2009.<ref name=\"official_candidate_order\">{{cite web |title=Publicaci\u00f3n del voto despeja inc\u00f3gnitas |publisher=Tiempo |year=2009 |url=http://tiempo.hn/secciones/politica/1956-publicacion-del-voto-despeja-incognitas |accessdate=2009-08-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5irH5p3mA?url=http://tiempo.hn/secciones/politica/1956-publicacion-del-voto-despeja-incognitas |archivedate=2009-08-07 |url-status=dead |language=es }}</ref>\n\nAn international human rights mission including, among others, [[:es:Nora Morales de Corti\u00f1as|Nora Corti\u00f1as]] of [[Mothers of the Plaza de Mayo]], reported that Carlos Humberto Reyes was injured on 30 July 2009 when \"the army and the special forces of the National Police of Honduras attacked thousands of pacific demonstrators, with fire weapons, wood and rubber projectiles and as well as tear gas, thrown even from helicopters.\"<ref name=\"laprensa_reyescandidate\">{{cite web |title=Defying threats, Zelaya supporters continue protests |work=[[La Prensa (Texas)|La Prensa]] |date=2009-07-31 |url=http://www.laprensasa.com/2.0/3/309/273599/America-in-English/Defying-threats-Zelaya-supporters-continue-protests.html |accessdate=2009-08-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713183835/http://www.laprensasa.com/2.0/3/309/273599/America-in-English/Defying-threats-Zelaya-supporters-continue-protests.html |archivedate=2011-07-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"enlazando_mission090730\">{{cite web|title=International Mission denounces the brutal repression of pacific demonstrations|publisher=Agencia Latinoamerica de Informaci\u00f3n|date=2009-07-30|url=http://www.alainet.org/active/32099|accessdate=2009-08-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724231655/http://www.alainet.org/active/32099|archivedate=2011-07-24|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\nOn 9 November 2009, following a national meeting of leaders of the [[National Resistance Front (Honduras)|National Resistance Front against the coup d'\u00e9tat]], Reyes declared the withdrawal of his candidacy, on the grounds of not legitimising the coup d'\u00e9tat and fraudulent elections.<ref name=\"tiempo_reyes_withdraws\">{{cite news |language=Spanish |title=Carlos H. Reyes anuncia su retiro de los comicios |date=2009-11-08 |publisher=[[El Tiempo (Honduras)]] |url=http://www.tiempo.hn/secciones/crisis-politica/7119-carlos-h-reyes-anuncia-su-retiro-de-los-comicios |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091112061320/http://www.tiempo.hn/secciones/crisis-politica/7119-carlos-h-reyes-anuncia-su-retiro-de-los-comicios |archivedate=2009-11-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"tribuna_reyes_withdraws\">{{cite news |language=Spanish |title=Carlos H. Reyes oficializa su renuncia |date=2009-11-09 |publisher=[[La Tribuna|La Tribuna (Honduras)]] |url=http://www.latribuna.hn/web2.0/?p=61658 |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030130239/http://www.latribuna.hn/web2.0/?p=61658 |archivedate=2010-10-30 |url-status=dead }}</ref> The Honduran newspapers ''El Tiempo'' and ''La Tribuna'' showed Reyes' right hand in a plaster cast.<ref name=\"tiempo_reyes_withdraws\" /><ref name=\"tribuna_reyes_withdraws\" />\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Carlos Reyes}}\n*[http://www.facebook.com/pages/Carlos-H-Reyes/185768405450?v=feed&story_fbid=236702365450&ref=mf Reyes' ] [[facebook]] entry\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Reyes, Carlos Humberto}}\n[[Category:Candidates for President of Honduras]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Honduran trade unionists]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{Honduras-politician-stub}}\n{{Trade-unionist-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Tassedethe", "label": "safe", "comment": "v2.02 - Repaired 1 link to disambiguation page -(You can help)-La Tribuna", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Humberto_Reyes"}
{"title_page": "Guilherme Costa Marques", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Guilherme\n| fullname = Guilherme Costa Marques\n| image = Met-legia (6).jpg\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1991|5|21|mf=yes}} \n| birth_place = [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil\n| height = {{height|meters=1.74}}\n| currentclub  = [[Trabzonspor]]<br/>(on loan from [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]])\n| clubnumber = 6\n| position = [[Midfielder (football)|Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 = 2008\u20132009\n| youthclubs1 = [[Para\u00edba do Sul Futebol Clube|Para\u00edba do Sul]]\n| youthyears2 = 2009\u20132010\n| youthclubs2 = [[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n| years1 = 2010\u20132015\n| years2 = 2010\u20132011\n| years3 = 2011\u20132012\n| years4 = 2012\u20132013\n| years5 = 2013\u20132015\n| years6 = 2015\u20132018\n| years7 = 2018\u2013\n| years8 = 2018\u20132019\n| years9 = 2019\u20132020\n| years10 = 2020\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n| clubs2 = \u2192 [[F.C. Vizela|Vizela]] (loan)\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] (loan)\n| clubs4 = [[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]]\n| clubs5 = \u2192 [[Legia Warsaw]] (loan)\n| clubs6 = [[Legia Warsaw]]\n| clubs7 = [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]]\n| clubs8 = \u2192 [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] (loan)\n| clubs9 = \u2192 [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] (loan)\n| clubs10 = \u2192 [[Trabzonspor]] (loan)\n| caps1 = 5\n| caps2 = 7\n| caps3 = 19\n| caps4 = 27\n| caps5 = 8\n| caps6 = 91\n| caps7 = 12\n| caps8 = 30\n| caps9 = 18\n| caps10 = 0\n| goals1 = 1\n| goals2 = 0\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 4\n| goals5 = 0\n| goals6 = 14\n| goals7 = 2\n| goals8 = 5\n| goals9 = 5\n| goals10 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| club-update = 18 December 2019\n| ntupdate =\n}}\n\n'''Guilherme Costa Marques''' known as '''Guilherme''' (born May 21, 1991) is a [[Brazil]]ian footballer who plays for Turkish club [[Trabzonspor]] on loan from [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]].\n\n==Club career==\n===SC Braga===\nBorn in [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil,<ref>{{cite news|title=Refor\u00e7o Guilherme agrada a Domingos|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/reforco-guilherme-agrada-a-domingos-593976|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=14 December 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme began playing futsal and trained at a football school.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\">{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-moje-motto-nigdy-sie-nie-poddawaj-49233|title=GUILHERME: MOJE MOTTO? NIGDY SI\u0118 NIE PODDAWAJ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 December 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126160436/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-moje-motto-nigdy-sie-nie-poddawaj-49233 |archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> As he grew older, began to take football seriously.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Guilherme then started out his career at [[Para\u00edba do Sul Futebol Clube|Para\u00edba do Sul]] before moving to Portugal, where he joined [[S.C. Braga|Braga]] in 2009 at age sixteen.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ojago\">{{cite news|title=Todo-o-terreno criativo e com alma guerreira|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/arquivo/2010/03/interior/todo-o-terreno-criativo-e-com-alma-guerreira-2562701.html|publisher=O Jogo|language=Portuguese|date=5 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Jean descartado|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/jean-descartado|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=18 September 2009|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final\"/> Immediately after joining the club, Guilherme was assigned to the youth team.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ojago\"/>\n\nIt wasn't until on 24 January 2010 when he made his SC Braga first team debut, starting the whole game, in a 4\u20131 win over [[U.D. Leiria|Leiria]].<ref>{{cite news|title=BRAGA GOLEIA LEIRIA POR 4-1 NO ADEUS \u00c0 PROVA|url=https://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/taca-da-liga/artigos/braga-goleia-leiria-por-4-1-no-adeus-a-prova|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=24 January 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He also appeared as an unused substitute bench in a league match against [[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|Vit\u00f3ria]] on 6 March 2010.<ref>{{cite news|title=V. Set\u00fabal-Sp. Braga, 0-0 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/v-setubal-sp-braga-0-0-cronica|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=6 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> For the remaining part of the 2009\u201310 season, Guilherme appeared in a number of matches as an unused substitute bench, as he made one appearance for the side.<ref>{{cite news|title=Miguel Garcia e Diogo Valente reintegrados|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/miguel-garcia-e-diogo-valente-reintegrados|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Solignac \u00e9 para ficar|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/solignac-e-para-ficar|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=29 April 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nAhead of the 2010\u201311 season, Guilherme was promoted to Braga's senior squad.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gale fica mais um ano|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/gale-fica-mais-um-ano|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=6 June 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> His first appearance of the season came on 21 August 2010, where he came on as a second\u2013half substitute, in a 0\u20130 draw against Vit\u00f3ria.<ref>{{cite news|title=V. Set\u00fabal-Sp. Braga, 0-0 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/sporting-braga-liga-vitoria-setubal-v-setubal-sp-braga-cronica-jornada-2-maisfutebol/520b8a6a3004bc615fd26e79.html|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=21 August 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> It wasn't until on 22 January 2011 when Guilherme scored his first goal of the season, in a 2\u20132 draw against Vit\u00f3ria.<ref>{{cite news|title=Domingos lamenta empate \"injusto\"|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/domingos-lamenta-empate-injusto-68062|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=22 January 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Eight days later, on 30 January 2011, he scored again in the [[2010\u201311 Ta\u00e7a da Liga#Third round|third round of Ta\u00e7a da Liga]], in a 4\u20130 win over [[F.C. Arouca|Arouca]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Ta\u00e7a da Liga: Arouca-Sp.Braga, 0-4 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/taca-da-liga-arouca-sp-braga-0-4-cronica|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=30 January 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2010\u201311 season, Guilherme went on to make eight appearances and scoring once in all competitions. During the season, he was linked a move away from SC Braga, as [[Juventus FC|Juventus]], [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]] and [[FC Barcelona]] were interested in signing him.<ref>{{cite news|title=Juventus quer Guilherme (SC Braga) no final da \u00e9poca|url=https://zerozero.co.mz/news.php?id=37020&redird=1|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=17 October 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Juventus avan\u00e7a para Guilherme|url=https://www.record.pt/internacional/detalhe/juventus-avanca-para-guilherme-721955|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=17 October 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nThe start of 2011\u201312 season saw Guilherme making one appearance, which came on 25 August 2011, where he set up a goal for [[Lima (footballer)|Lima]] in a 2\u20132 draw against [[BSC Young Boys]] in the second leg of the UEFA Qualification Play\u2013Off and saw the club go through to the Group Stage, thanks to away goal.<ref>{{cite news|title=QUALIFICA\u00c7\u00c3O FELIZ COM \"SOFRIMENTO\" \u00c0 MISTURA|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/liga-europa/artigos/qualificacao-feliz-com-sofrimento-a-mistura|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=25 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After spending the 2011\u201312 season on loan at Gil Vicente, Guilherme was sent to the [[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]] team for the whole 2012\u201313 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Arranque com cinco caras novas|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/arranque-com-cinco-caras-novas-765360|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 July 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At Braga B team, Guilherme received a handful of playing time despite being called up from the senior team.<ref>{{cite news|title=Peseiro chama An\u00edbal e Guilherme|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/braga/noticias/interior/peseiro-chama-anibal-e-guilherme-2838715.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=20 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Convocat\u00f3ria com Haas|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/braga/noticias/interior/convocatoria-com-haas-2851796.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=27 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=A oportunidade dos jovens|url=https://www.record.pt/opiniao/cronistas/antonio-oliveira/detalhe/a-oportunidade-dos-jovens-796876|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=3 January 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He also helped the side reach the final of [[2012 Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final|final]] against [[S.L. Benfica]], which they lost 2\u20131.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final\">{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-mam-nature-wojownika-39238|title=GUILHERME: MAM NATUR\u0118 WOJOWNIKA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122211025/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-mam-nature-wojownika-39238|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sent\u2013off on two occasions,<ref>{{cite news|title=Tondela-Braga B, 2-1: Piojo operou reviravolta|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/tondela-braga-b-2-1-piojo-operou-reviravolta-776408|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 September 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Penafiel-Sp. Braga B, 2-0: Ferreira e Robson resolvem|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/penafiel-sp-braga-b-2-0-ferreira-e-robson-resolvem-781878|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=7 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme went on to make twenty\u2013six appearances and scoring four times for Braga B team.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sp. Braga B-U. Madeira, 1-1: Minhotos continuam sem vencer|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/sp-braga-b-u-madeira-1-1-minhotos-continuam-sem-vencer-775186|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=26 August 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Leix\u00f5es-Sp. Braga B, 1-1: Jovem Kizito salva anfitri\u00f5es|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/leixoes-sp-braga-b-1-1-jovem-kizito-salva-anfitrioes-779644|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=23 September 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Braga B j\u00e1 v\u00ea a salva\u00e7\u00e3o|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/2a-liga/noticias/interior/braga-b-ja-ve-a-salvacao-3163274.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=12 April 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nIt was announced on 19 June 2013 that Guilherme's future at the SC Braga was in doubt, leading the club become more interested in signing him.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme roda outra vez|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-roda-outra-vez-828276|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=19 June 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Canarinhos querem Guilherme emprestado|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/estoril/detalhe/canarinhos-querem-guilherme-emprestado-828535|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=20 June 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He spent the rest of the year, training for the reserve side.<ref name=\"Guilherme 2013\">{{cite news|title=Guilherme w Legii. Wolny zawodnik, a jednak wypo\u017cyczony [KOMENTARZ]|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-w-legii-wolny-zawodnik-a-jednak-wypozyczony-komentarz/ar/9577996|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=15 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> It was announced on 10 January 2014 that Guilherme was expected to leave SC Braga, either having his contract terminated or on loan.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme e Lu\u00eds Alberto despedem-se do SC Braga|url=https://zerozero.co.mz/news.php?id=131189|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=10 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n====Loan Spells====\nIn the first part of the following season, Guilherme was loaned to [[LigaPro|Segunda Liga]] side [[F.C. Vizela|Vizela]], where he made seven appearances for the side.<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\">{{cite news|title=Calciomercato Benevento, chi \u00e8 Guilherme: estro e fantasia|url=https://www.goal.com/it/notizie/calciomercato-benevento-chi-e-guilherme-estro-e-fantasia/rb7vusy46ni518lbodls2ib9r|publisher=Goal.com|language=Italian|date=11 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nFor the 2011\u201312 season, Guilherme was loaned out to [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] for the rest of the season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-cedido-ao-gil-vicente-714899|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=31 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899|title=Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente|publisher=Record XL|language=Portuguese|date=31 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143300/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme made his Gil Vicente debut on 16 September 2011, where he came on as a second-half substitute, in a 2\u20132 draw against [[S.C. Olhanense|Olhanense]].<ref>{{cite news|title=GIL EMPATA NOS MINUTOS FINAIS|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/primeira-liga/artigos/gil-empata-nos-minutos-finais|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=16 September 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> The following month, on 27 October 2011 in the Ta\u00e7a da Liga campaign, he scored his first goal for Gil Vicente, scoring from a penalty, in a 2\u20131 loss against [[C.F. Os Belenenses|Belenenses]].<ref>{{cite news|title=BELENENSES VENCE GIL VICENTE COM PEN\u00c1LTI TARDIO|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/taca-da-liga/artigos/belenenses-vence-gil-vicente-com-penalti-tardio|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=27 October 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Throughout the 2011-2012 season, Guilherme went on to make twenty\u2013six appearances and scoring once in all competitions.\n\n===Legia Warsaw===\nOn 14 January 2014, it was announced that Guilherme was loaned out to [[Legia Warsaw]] for the next twelve months.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-trafi-do-legii-39220|title=GUILHERME TRAFI DO LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=13 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119151109/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-trafi-do-legii-39220|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-podpisal-kontrakt-hd-39239|title=GUILHERME PODPISA\u0141 KONTRAKT (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043157/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-podpisal-kontrakt-hd-39239|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme 2013\"/> Upon joining the club, Guilherme became the twelve [[Brazil]]ian player to join Legia Warsaw.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dwunasty-brazylijczyk-w-legii-39243|title=DWUNASTY BRAZYLIJCZYK W LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122211011/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dwunasty-brazylijczyk-w-legii-39243|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Legia Warsaw debut on 14 February 2014, where he started the match before being substituted in the 74th minutes, in a 1\u20130 win over [[Korona Kielce]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Znamy sk\u0142ady na mecz Legia - Korona. Debiut Guilherme i Chi\u017cniczenki!|url=https://gol24.pl/znamy-sklady-na-mecz-legia-korona-debiut-guilherme-i-chizniczenki/ar/9575666|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=15 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After making another appearance, he, however, suffered a ruptured intraarticular ligament initiation in the ankle that saw sidelined until the end of the 2013\u201314 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme kontuzjowany na treningu|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-kontuzjowany-na-treningu/ar/9574516|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme nie zagra przez cztery tygodnie|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-nie-zagra-przez-cztery-tygodnie/ar/9574230|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=28 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia nie wyda miliona na Guilherme|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-nie-wyda-miliona-na-guilherme/pf39v66|publisher=Fakt|language=Polish|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> By the time he suffered an ruptured his ankle, Guilherme went on to make two appearances for the side this season. Despite this, he went on to win February's Player of the Month by the club's supporters.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://legia.com/news,40111-guilherme_pilkarzem_miesiaca.html|title=Guilherme pi\u0142karzem miesi\u0105ca|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 March 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016113321/https://legia.com/news,40111-guilherme_pilkarzem_miesiaca.html|archivedate=16 October 2014|url-status=live}}</ref> During his injury, the club went on to win the league.\n\nAt the start of the 2014\u201315 season, Guilherme remained sidelined from the first team, due to suffering from injury.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-w-rzymie-kadrowicze-wracaja-do-zdrowia-43459|title=GUILHERME W RZYMIE, KADROWICZE WRACAJ\u0104 DO ZDROWIA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 September 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122215515/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-w-rzymie-kadrowicze-wracaja-do-zdrowia-43459|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> It wasn't until on 17 October 2014 when he made his return from injury, coming on as a substitute, where Legia Warsaw beat [[Lechia Gda\u0144sk]] 1\u20130.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/instynkt-s-n-ajpera-legia-lechia-1-0-44248|title=INSTYNKT S(N)AJPERA. LEGIA - LECHIA 1:0!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=17 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126123623/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/instynkt-s-n-ajpera-legia-lechia-1-0-44248|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/powrot-guilherme-po-238-dniach-44254|title=POWR\u00d3T GUILHERME PO 238 DNIACH|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=18 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126123621/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/powrot-guilherme-po-238-dniach-44254|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Four days later, on 22 October 2014, he made his first start as a left\u2013back since returning from injury, in a 1\u20130 win over [[FC Metalist Kharkiv|Metalist Kharkiv]] in the group stage of the UEFA Europa League.<ref>{{cite news|title=Europa League: Legia Warsaw continue fine form with win over Metalist Kharkiv|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9529454/europa-league-metalist-kharkiv-0-legia-warsaw-1|publisher=Sky Sports|date=22 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Since returning to the first team from injury, Guilherme regained his first team place, playing in the left\u2013back position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-legia-zagra-w-belgii-na-luzie-44781|title=DZIENNIKARZE: LEGIA ZAGRA W BELGII NA LUZIE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 November 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131029/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-legia-zagra-w-belgii-na-luzie-44781|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-awansujemy-z-1-miejsca-44997|title=DZIENNIKARZE: AWANSUJEMY Z 1. MIEJSCA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=11 December 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131736/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-awansujemy-z-1-miejsca-44997|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/brzyski-czy-guilherme-zacieta-walka-na-lewej-obronie-45591|title=BRZYSKI CZY GUILHERME? ZACI\u0118TA WALKA NA LEWEJ OBRONIE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=9 February 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126132149/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/brzyski-czy-guilherme-zacieta-walka-na-lewej-obronie-45591|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The following month on 14 January 2015, it was announced that Guilherme signed for Legia Warsaw on a permanent basis, signing a three\u2013year contract.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme wykupiony, kontrakt na 3,5 roku|url=https://www.onet.pl/?srcc=ucs&pid=58255111-be50-5d50-8ee3-bf6dc6133366&sid=4390aa51-c69b-410e-bc0a-a3c3c7c23e1d|publisher=Onet.pl|language=Polish|date=14 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-na-dluzej-w-legii-45457|title=GUILHERME NA D\u0141U\u017bEJ W LEGII!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=30 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131939/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-na-dluzej-w-legii-45457|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After losing his place by the returning [[Tomasz Brzyski]], Guilherme regained his first team place in attacking position, although he occasionally played at the left\u2013back position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-wisla-46038|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z WIS\u0141\u0104?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=15 March 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126135606/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-wisla-46038|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/berg-presja-jest-z-nami-zawsze-hd-46251|title=BERG: PRESJA JEST Z NAMI ZAWSZE (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=3 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126140028/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/berg-presja-jest-z-nami-zawsze-hd-46251|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-najwazniejsze-zeby-legia-osiagala-swoje-cele-hd-46252|title=GUILHERME: NAJWA\u017bNIEJSZE, \u017bEBY LEGIA OSI\u0104GA\u0141A SWOJE CELE (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=3 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126140030/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-najwazniejsze-zeby-legia-osiagala-swoje-cele-hd-46252|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His first goal for the club came on 29 April 2015, where he scored an equaliser, in a 2\u20131 win over [[Pogo\u0144 Szczecin]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia przegrywa\u0142a, ale ogra\u0142a Pogo\u0144. Mistrz Polski liderem po podziale punkt\u00f3w|url=https://gol24.pl/legia-przegrywala-ale-ograla-pogon-mistrz-polski-liderem-po-podziale-punktow/ar/9525284|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=29 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Three days later, on 2 May 2015, Guilherme helped the beat [[Lech Pozna\u0144]], who went on to win the league, 2\u20131 in the [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup#Final|Polish Cup]] final.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/lech-legia-1-2-puchar-jest-nasz-46595|title=LECH - LEGIA 1:2. PUCHAR JEST NASZ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=2 May 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126141256/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/lech-legia-1-2-puchar-jest-nasz-46595|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/tytul-nie-dla-legii-zabraklo-jednego-punktu-47035|title=TYTU\u0141 NIE DLA LEGII. ZABRAK\u0141O JEDNEGO PUNKTU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 June 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142959/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/tytul-nie-dla-legii-zabraklo-jednego-punktu-47035|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sidelined several times later in the 2014\u201315 season,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-ruchem-44484|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z RUCHEM?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=2 November 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126130618/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-ruchem-44484|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-podbeskidziem-45877|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z PODBESKIDZIEM?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 March 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126134500/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-podbeskidziem-45877|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-pogonia-46858|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z POGONI\u0104?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=23 May 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142459/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-pogonia-46858|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme went on to make thirty appearances and scoring once for the side.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/podsumowujemy-sezon-wystepy-minuty-47051|title=PODSUMOWUJEMY SEZON: WYST\u0118PY/MINUTY|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=9 June 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142943/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/podsumowujemy-sezon-wystepy-minuty-47051|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAt the start of the 2015\u201316 season, Guilherme remained in the first team regular for the side, where he played in the right\u2013wing position despite competing with [[Micha\u0142 Kucharczyk]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-prasie-po-klasyku-47771|title=W PRASIE PO KLASYKU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=10 August 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126150450/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-prasie-po-klasyku-47771|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|title=Guilherme: Plotki o zmianie trenera nie mia\u0142y na nas wp\u0142ywu|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-plotki-o-zmianie-trenera-nie-mialy-na-nas-wplywu/ar/9508176|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=2 October 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-wszyscy-pracujemy-na-sukces-naszej-legii-49427|title=GUILHERME: WSZYSCY PRACUJEMY NA SUKCES NASZEJ LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=10 December 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126162614/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-wszyscy-pracujemy-na-sukces-naszej-legii-49427|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He started the season well when he scored in the second leg of the UEFA Europa League Qualification against [[FC Boto\u0219ani]], in a 3\u20130 win to advance to the next round.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/botosani-legia-0-3-wojskowi-w-iii-rundzie-47553|title=BOTOSANI - LEGIA 0:3. 'WOJSKOWI' W III RUNDZIE!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=23 July 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126145259/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/botosani-legia-0-3-wojskowi-w-iii-rundzie-47553|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> A month later, on 27 August 2015, Guilherme scored again in the play\u2013offs round of the UEFA Europa League, in a 3\u20132 win over [[FC Zorya Luhansk|Zorya Luhansk]] to advance to the Group Stage.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legionisci-o-meczu-z-zoria-48025|title=LEGIONI\u015aCI O MECZU Z ZORI\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 August 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126153224/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legionisci-o-meczu-z-zoria-48025|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Three days later, on 30 August 2015, he scored his first league goal of the season, in a 1\u20131 draw against [[Jagiellonia Bia\u0142ystok]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/1-1-w-bialymstoku-remis-w-ostatnim-meczu-przed-przerwa-48068|title=1:1 W BIA\u0141YMSTOKU. REMIS W OSTATNIM MECZU PRZED PRZERW\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=30 August 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126153646/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/1-1-w-bialymstoku-remis-w-ostatnim-meczu-przed-przerwa-48068|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His performance at Legia Warsaw attracted interests from Serie A side [[Inter Milan]], but the move never happened.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme na celowniku Interu Mediolan!|url=http://sportowefakty.wp.pl/pilka-nozna/558360/guilherme-na-celowniku-interu-mediolan|publisher=Sportowe Fakty|language=Polish|date=5 November 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After being sidelined on two separate matches between late\u2013February and early\u2013March,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-kucharczyka-i-guilherme-z-ruchem-50430|title=BEZ KUCHARCZYKA I GUILHERME Z RUCHEM|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=21 February 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126170411/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-kucharczyka-i-guilherme-z-ruchem-50430|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-wraca-na-zwycieska-sciezke-50684|title=LEGIA WRACA NA ZWYCI\u0118SK\u0104 \u015aCIE\u017bK\u0118!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 March 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126171013/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-wraca-na-zwycieska-sciezke-50684|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme scored on his return from the sidelined on 12 March 2016, in a 2\u20131 win over [[KS Cracovia (football)|KS Cracovia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-warszawa-wciaz-na-tronie-50799|title=LEGIA WARSZAWA WCI\u0104\u017b NA TRONIE!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 March 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126171554/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-warszawa-wciaz-na-tronie-50799|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The following month, he scored the second leg of the semi\u2013final of the Polish Cup, in a 2\u20131 win over [[Zawisza Bydgoszcz]] to reach the final; which they beat Lech Pozna\u0144 again in the [[2015\u201316 Polish Cup#Final|Polish Cup]] final for the second time in a row.<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia Warsaw dope\u0142ni\u0142a formalno\u015bci|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-dopelnila-formalnosci/9qt9ez3|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=6 April 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Fina\u0142 Pucharu Polski: Legia Warszawa lepsza od Lecha Pozna\u0144. Skandal na trybunach|url=https://www.newsweek.pl/sport/final-pucharu-polski-2016-legia-warszawa-lech-poznan-bramki/hde35st|publisher=Newsweek Polska|language=Polish|date=2 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After adding his eighth goal of the season against [[Piast Gliwice]] on 8 May 2016, Guilherme helped the side win the league.<ref>{{cite news|title=Deklasacja w Warszawie. Znamy mistrza Polski?|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-warszawa-piast-gliwice-40-legia-jest-juz-blisko-mistrzostwa-polski-jesli-w/8s1q3qm#slajd-1|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=8 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia Warszawa mistrzem Polski!|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/ekstraklasa-legia-warszawa-pogon-szczecin-gra-o-mistrzostwo-polski-relacja-live-na/eezdvf0|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=15 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2015\u201316 season, he went on to make 55 appearances and scoring 8 times in all competitions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-to-jest-legia-presja-to-norma-51763|title=GUILHERME: TO JEST LEGIA, PRESJA TO NORMA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=20 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174623/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-to-jest-legia-presja-to-norma-51763|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAt the start of the 2016\u201317 season, Guilherme started the season when he scored the club's first goal of the season, as Legia Warrsaw lost 4\u20131 to Lech Pozna\u0144 in the [[2016 Polish SuperCup|Polish SuperCup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przegrana-legii-w-meczu-o-superpuchar-52355|title=PRZEGRANA LEGII W MECZU O SUPERPUCHAR|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126195745/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przegrana-legii-w-meczu-o-superpuchar-52355|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> But he soon suffered a shoulder injury during a 2\u20130 win over [[H\u0160K Zrinjski Mostar|Zrinjski Mostar]] in the second leg of the UEFA Champions League second round and was sidelined for a month.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme czeka operacja i d\u0142uga przerwa w grze|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-czeka-operacja-i-dluga-przerwa-w-grze/ar/10430060|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=21 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Kontuzja barku Guilherme. \"Pozostaje modli\u0107 si\u0119, by to nie by\u0142o nic powa\u017cnego\"|url=https://gol24.pl/kontuzja-barku-guilherme-pozostaje-modlic-sie-by-to-nie-bylo-nic-powaznego/ar/10426080|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=20 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He then made his return from injury on 20 August 2016 against [[Arka Gdynia]], where he came on as a second-half substitute and set up a goal for [[Kasper H\u00e4m\u00e4l\u00e4inen]], in a 3\u20131 loss.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-arka-1-3-52914|title=LEGIA WARSAW - ARKA GDYNIA 1: 3|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=20 August 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126201834/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-arka-1-3-52914|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Since returning from a shoulder injury, Guilherme regained his first team place, playing in the right\u2013wing position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-bedzie-coraz-lepiej-52445|title=GUILHERME: B\u0118DZIE CORAZ LEPIEJ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126195734/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-bedzie-coraz-lepiej-52445|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia Warszawa \u2013 Lech Pozna\u0144. Nenad Bjelica: Kogo chcia\u0142bym wykupi\u0107 z Legii? Nikogo|url=http://poznan.wyborcza.pl/poznan/1,36006,20873218,legia-warszawa-lech-poznan-nenad-bjelica-kogo-chcialbym.html|publisher=Wyborcza Poznan|language=Polish|date=22 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 1 October 2016, Guilherme scored a brace, scoring from the first and second goal of the game, in a 3\u20130 win over [[Lechia Gda\u0144sk]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przebudzenie-mistrzow-53417|title=PRZEBUDZENIE MISTRZ\u00d3W|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126204204/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przebudzenie-mistrzow-53417|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Then, on 7 December 2016, he scored his first UEFA Champions League goal, in a 1\u20130 win over [[Sporting CP]], their first win of the UEFA Champions League's Group Stage.<ref>{{cite news|title=Mecz Legia \u2013 Sporting. Waleczna Legia pokona\u0142a Sporting! Jest trzecie miejsce i Liga Europy|url=https://gol24.pl/mecz-legia-sporting-waleczna-legia-pokonala-sporting-jest-trzecie-miejsce-i-liga-europy/ar/11553310|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=7 December 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> The following month saw the club opened a contract negotiation to convince Guilherme stay at the club beyond 2018, whose contract was expected to expire.<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia straci Guilherme?|url=https://gol24.pl/legia-straci-guilherme/ar/11660040|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=5 January 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Later in the 2016\u201317 season, he helped the club win the league for the second time in a row on the last game of the season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mniej-biegania-wiecej-taktyki-55281|title=MNIEJ BIEGANIA, WI\u0118CEJ TAKTYKI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=26 April 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126230915/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mniej-biegania-wiecej-taktyki-55281|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzem-polski-jest-legia-55566|title=MISTRZEM POLSKI JEST LEGIA!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 June 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126223721/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzem-polski-jest-legia-55566|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sidelined later in the 2016\u201317 season,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-radovicia-i-guilherme-z-wisla-54069|title=BEZ RADOVICIA I GUILHERME Z WIS\u0141\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=28 November 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126224900/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-radovicia-i-guilherme-z-wisla-54069|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-w-czwartkowej-prasie-i-mediach-54102|title=LEGIA W CZWARTKOWEJ PRASIE I MEDIACH|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 December 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126224909/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-w-czwartkowej-prasie-i-mediach-54102|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-korona-ciekawostki-55211|title=LEGIA - KORONA: CIEKAWOSTKI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 April 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126230904/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-korona-ciekawostki-55211|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> he went on to make 41 appearances and scoring 7 times in all competitions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzowie-z-l3-oni-zdobyli-tytul-55542|title=MISTRZOWIE Z \u01413 - ONI ZDOBYLI TYTU\u0141|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=4 June 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126232429/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzowie-z-l3-oni-zdobyli-tytul-55542|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAhead of the 2017\u201318 season, Guilherme was linked away from the club, as Sporting CP and [[Trabzonspor]] were among interested.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sporting Lizbona zg\u0142asza si\u0119 po pi\u0142karza Legii|url=https://gol24.pl/sporting-lizbona-zglasza-sie-po-pilkarza-legii/ar/12063616|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=10 May 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Wyprzeda\u017c w Legii? Guilherme na celowniku Trabzonsporu|url=https://gol24.pl/wyprzedaz-w-legii-guilherme-na-celowniku-trabzonsporu/ar/12219891|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=28 June 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Despite this, Guilherme stayed at the club and started the season when he set up the equaliser for [[Thibault Moulin]] to score against Arka Gdynia in the [[2017 Polish SuperCup|Polish SuperCup]] on 7 July 2017; leading the match to extra\u2013time and penalty shoot\u2013out, where he successfully converted the shootout, but lost 4\u20133 in the penalty shoot\u2013out.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zdjac-klatwe-superpucharu-55812|title=ZDJ\u0104\u0106 KL\u0104TW\u0118 SUPERPUCHARU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194805/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zdjac-klatwe-superpucharu-55812|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He then scored in both legs of the UEFA Champions League Second Round Qualification against [[IFK Mariehamn]] in a 9\u20130 on aggregate to advance to the next round.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pierwszy-krok-wykonany-55859|title=PIERWSZY KROK WYKONANY!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194743/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pierwszy-krok-wykonany-55859|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pogrom-i-pewny-awans-do-iii-rundy-eliminacji-lm-uefa-55908|title=POGROM I PEWNY AWANS DO III RUNDY ELIMINACJI LM UEFA!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194748/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pogrom-i-pewny-awans-do-iii-rundy-eliminacji-lm-uefa-55908|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> However, Guilherme was sidelined for a month after suffering a knee injury during a 1\u20131 draw against [[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff Tiraspol]] in a UEFA Europa League Play\u2013Off Round match in the first leg.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/kilka-tygodni-przerwy-guilherme-56257|title=KILKA TYGODNI PRZERWY GUILHERME|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 August 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129203849/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/kilka-tygodni-przerwy-guilherme-56257|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After returning to training, he didn't make his return to the first team on 1 October 2017, coming on as a second-half substitute, in a 3\u20130 loss against Lech Poznan.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/trening-z-guilherme-56513|title=TRENING Z GUILHERME|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=15 September 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129203846/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/trening-z-guilherme-56513|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-poznaniu-na-smutno-56630|title=W POZNANIU NA SMUTNO|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 October 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210447/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-poznaniu-na-smutno-56630|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme then scored two goals in two matches between on 9 December 2017 and 12 December 2017 against [[Bruk-Bet Termalica Nieciecza]] and [[Piast Gliwice]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Lotto Ekstraklasa. Hamalainen zata\u0144czy\u0142 z Termalik\u0105, G\u00f3rnik poczu\u0142 oddech Legii na plecach|url=https://gol24.pl/lotto-ekstraklasa-hamalainen-zatanczyl-z-termalika-gornik-poczul-oddech-legii-na-plecach/ar/12752647|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=9 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zadanie-wykonane-legia-znowu-liderem-57222|title=ZADANIE WYKONANE, LEGIA ZNOWU LIDEREM!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210346/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zadanie-wykonane-legia-znowu-liderem-57222|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> It was announced on 8 December 2017 that Guilherme was not signing a new contract with Legia Warsaw and expected to leave the club when the transfer window opens next month.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-przedluzy-kontraktu-z-legia-warszawa-57190|title=GUILHERME NIE PRZED\u0141U\u017bY KONTRAKTU Z LEGI\u0104 WARSZAWA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=8 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210415/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-przedluzy-kontraktu-z-legia-warszawa-57190|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His last appearance, which also coincidentally turns out to be his 150th appearance for Legia Warsaw, came on 16 December 2017, in a 2\u20130 loss against [[Wis\u0142a P\u0142ock]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/150-mecz-guilherme-w-legii-57264|title=150. MECZ GUILHERME W LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210339/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/150-mecz-guilherme-w-legii-57264|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After the match, he made a farewell statements, thanking the club during his four years spell there.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/gui-dziekujemy-57247|title=GUI \u2013 DZI\u0118KUJEMY!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210336/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/gui-dziekujemy-57247|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-bylo-to-pozegnanie-o-jakim-marzylem-57278|title=GUILHERME: NIE BY\u0141O TO PO\u017bEGNANIE, O JAKIM MARZY\u0141EM|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210334/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-bylo-to-pozegnanie-o-jakim-marzylem-57278|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> By the time he departed the club, Guilherme's contribution to the club winning the league this season, where he made 22 appearances and scoring five times, earned him a medal.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/oni-zdobyli-14-tytul-mistrza-polski-58735|title=ONI ZDOBYLI 14. TYTU\u0141 MISTRZA POLSKI!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=22 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210328/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/oni-zdobyli-14-tytul-mistrza-polski-58735|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nDuring his time at Legia Warsaw, Guilherme made 150 appearances and scoring 21 times, as he helped the side win the Polish Cup on two occasions and the league on three occasions.<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/najbardziej-utytulowani-legionisci-58861|title=NAJBARDZIEJ UTYTU\u0141OWANI LEGIONI\u015aCI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 June 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210325/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/najbardziej-utytulowani-legionisci-58861|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He was also the club's fan favourite, due to his dribbling and shooting skills.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-czyli-pomocnik-z-prawdziwego-zdarzenia-51464|title=GUILHERME, CZYLI POMOCNIK Z PRAWDZIWEGO ZDARZENIA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 April 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174716/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-czyli-pomocnik-z-prawdziwego-zdarzenia-51464|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n===Benevento===\nWith his contract not being renewed, Guilherme was linked a move to [[Serie A]] side [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]], who was at 20th place at the time, and was looking for reinforcements to help the side avoid relegation.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento, accelerata per Guilherme del Legia Varsavia|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-accelerata-per-guilherme-del-legia-varsavia-1051634|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=8 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Benevento, accordo con Guilherme. De Ceglie continua il provino|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-accordo-con-guilherme-de-ceglie-continua-il-provino-1052959|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=12 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 16 December 2017, Italian media Tutto Mercato Web reported that Guilherme agreed a deal to join the club.<ref>{{cite news|title=ESCLUSIVA TMW - Benevento, l'ag. di Guilherme a Varsavia|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/esclusiva-tmw-benevento-l-ag-di-guilherme-a-varsavia-1054463|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> However, his move to Benevento was delayed over paperwork issues.<ref>{{cite news|title=ESCLUSIVA TMW - Benevento, Guilherme dopo la sosta: documenti da finire|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/esclusiva-tmw-benevento-guilherme-dopo-la-sosta-documenti-da-finire-1061359|publisher=Tutto Mercato|language=Italian|date=5 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Eventually, it was announced on 19 January 2018 that he joined Benevento.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.beneventocalcio.club/news/notizie/910/arrivato-il-transfer-per-guilherme.shtml|title=ARRIVATO IL TRANSFER PER GUILHERME.|publisher=Benevento Calcio|language=Italian|date=19 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190130192758/https://www.beneventocalcio.club/news/notizie/910/arrivato-il-transfer-per-guilherme.shtml|archivedate=30 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Benevento debut on 21 January 2018 against [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]], where he started the whole game, in a 3\u20130 loss.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bologna-Benevento 3-0: Destro, De Maio e Dzemaili fanno ripartire i rossobl\u00f9|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2018/01/21/news/bologna_batte_benevento-186977409/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=21 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After his making his debut, Eurosport gave his performance 6/10, commenting: \"Encouraging the performance of the last arrived; in the first part of the race he sows panic in the opposing defence.\"<ref>{{cite news|title=Le pagelle di Bologna-Benevento 3-0|url=https://it.eurosport.com/calcio/serie-a/2017-2018/le-pagelle-di-bologna-benevento-3-0_sto6491768/story.shtml|publisher=Eurosport|language=Italian|date=21 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> His first goal came on 11 February 2018, in a 5\u20132 loss against [[A.S. Roma|Roma]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Roma-Benevento 5-2: Under doppietta, Di Francesco scavalca la Lazio|url=https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Serie-A/Roma/11-02-2018/roma-benevento-5-2-doppietta-under-francesco-scavalca-lazio-250216869964.shtml|publisher=La Gazzetta Dello Sport|language=Italian|date=11 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> A month later on 31 March 2018, he scored again, which saw Benevento lost 6\u20132 loss against [[SS Lazio|Lazio]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Lazio-Benevento 6-2: i biancocelesti prima soffrono, poi dilagano|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2018/03/31/news/lazio_batte_benevento-192674613/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=31 March 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> However, Guilherme suffered ankle injury during a 2\u20132 draw against [[U.S. Sassuolo Calcio|Sassuolo]] on 15 April 2018 and was expected to be out for the rest of the season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento, stagione finita per Guilherme|url=https://sport.virgilio.it/benevento-stagione-finita-per-guilherme-40771|publisher=Sport Virgilio|language=Italian|date=16 April 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> While on the sidelined, the club were relegated to Serie B after spending one season at Serie A.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento relegated to Serie B|url=https://www.football-italia.net/120310/benevento-relegated-serie-b|publisher=Football Italia|date=22 April 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> But on the last game of the season, he made his return from injury on 20 May 2018 against [[A.C. ChievoVerona|Chievo]], starting the whole game, in a 1\u20130 loss.<ref>{{cite news|title=Chievo-Benevento 1-0: Inglese saluta con il gol salvezza|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/chievo/2018/05/20/news/chievo-benevento_1-0_festa_gialloblu_inglese_saluta_con_il_gol-196918662/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=20 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2017\u201318 season, Guilherme went on to make twelve appearances and scoring two times in all competitions.\n\nFollowing the club's relegation, Guilherme was linked a move away from Benevento despite being keen on playing in Serie B next season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Tre club di A si muovono per Guilherme|url=https://sport.virgilio.it/tre-club-di-a-si-muovono-per-guilherme-47238|publisher=Sport Virgilio|language=Italian|date=10 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme-Benevento \u00e8 rottura, Foggia: \"Chi non ha motivazioni pu\u00f2 stare a casa\"|url=https://www.anteprima24.it/benevento/guilherme-benevento-rottura/|publisher=Ante Prima|language=Italian|date=5 July 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme zbuntowa\u0142 si\u0119 w Benevento. By\u0142y gracz Legii ma ofert\u0119 z Serie A|url=http://futbol.pl/news/560977_Guilherme_zbuntowal_sie_w_Benevento_Byly_gracz_Legii_ma_oferte_z_Serie_A|publisher=Futbol.pl|language=Polish|date=18 July 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Benevento, Guilherme: \"Non ho problemi a restare anche in B\"|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-guilherme-non-ho-problemi-a-restare-anche-in-b-1082733|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=28 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n====Yeni Malatyaspor (loan)====\nIt was announced on 4 August 2018 that Guilherme joined [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] on a season\u2013long deal for the 2018\u201319 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme, Yeni Malatyaspor'da|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/guilherme-yeni-malatyasporda-40918382|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=4 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Guilherme\u2019ye imza attirdi|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/yeni-malatyaspor-guilherme-ye-evkur-yeni-malatyaspor-2718967-skorerhaber/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=4 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Yeni Malatyaspor debut in the opening game of the season, where he started the match before being substituted in the 81st minutes, in a 3\u20131 win over [[G\u00f6ztepe S.K.|G\u00f6ztepe]].<ref>{{cite news|title=G\u00f6ztepe - Evkur Malatyaspor: 1-3 (\u00d6ZET)|url=http://tr.beinsports.com/haber/goztepe-evkur-malatyaspor|publisher=Bein Sports|language=Turkish|date=12 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> In a follow up match against [[Fenerbah\u00e7e S.K. (football)|Fenerbah\u00e7e]] seven days later on 19 August 2018, he played a vital role for the side when he set up a goal for [[Danijel Aleksi\u0107]] to score the only goal in the game, in a 1\u20130 victory.<ref>{{cite news|title=Fenerbah\u00e7e gols\u00fcz, puans\u0131z, \u0131\u015f\u0131ks\u0131z!|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/fenerbahce-golsuz-puansiz-isiksiz-40932012|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=19 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 15 September 2018, Guilherme scored his first goal for the club, in a 2\u20131 loss against [[Be\u015fikta\u015f J.K.|Be\u015fikta\u015f]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Be\u015fikta\u015f 10 ki\u015fiyle kazand\u0131|url=https://www.sabah.com.tr/spor/futbol/2018/09/16/canli-besiktas-evkur-yeni-malatyaspor|publisher=Sabah|language=Turkish|date=16 September 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Then, on 9 November 2018, he scored a brace and set up two of the other three goals, in a 5\u20130 win over [[Trabzonspor]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Trabzonspor farkl\u0131 yenildi|url=https://www.sabah.com.tr/spor/futbol/2018/11/10/trabzonspor-zorlu-deplasmanda|publisher=Sabah|language=Turkish|date=10 November 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Since joining the club, he quickly established himself in the starting eleven and impressed the management with his display.<ref>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor'un \"yenileri\" g\u00f6z dolduruyor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/yeni-malatyasporun-yenileri-goz-dolduruyor-40968321|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=26 September 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Malatyaspor'da Guilherme harekat\u0131 ba\u015flad\u0131!|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/malatyasporda-guilherme-harekati-basladi-41059408|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=21 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: 'Art\u0131k teknoloji futbola girdi. Bu duruma herkesin al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131 gerekiyor'|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/guilherme-artik-teknoloji-futbola-girdi-bu-duruma-herkesin-alismasi-gerekiyor-40977714|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=5 October 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Despite suffering an injury and facing suspension at separate times towards the end of the year,<ref>{{cite news|title=Malatyaspor, Antalyaspor'a haz\u0131rlan\u0131yor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/malatyaspor-antalyaspora-hazirlaniyor-41048549|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=12 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Kas\u0131mpa\u015fa ma\u00e7\u0131na haz\u0131rlan\u0131yor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/malatya/yeni-malatyaspor-kasimpasa-macina-hazirlaniyor-41025291|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=20 November 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme then scored again and was sent\u2013off later in the game, in a 1\u20131 draw against [[Bursaspor]] on 23 December 2018.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bursaspor Yeni Malatya'y\u0131 elinden ka\u00e7\u0131rd\u0131|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/bursaspor-yeni-malatyayi-elinden-kacirdi-41061219|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=23 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After suffering an injury and facing suspension at separate times once again in early\u2013January,<ref>{{cite news|title=\"Sonuna Kadar Tak\u0131m\u0131n Ba\u015f\u0131nda Duraca\u011f\u0131m\"|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/sonuna-kadar-takimin-basinda-duracagim-malatya-yerelhaber-3229067/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=15 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Fenerbah\u00e7e'ye Konuk Olacak|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/yeni-malatyaspor-fenerbahce-ye-konuk-malatya-yerelhaber-3234926/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=27 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme made his return to the first team on 28 January 2019, in a 3\u20132 loss against Fenerbah\u00e7e.<ref>{{cite news|title=Fenerbah\u00e7e uykudan uyand\u0131: 3-2|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/fenerbahce-uykusundan-uyandi-41097085|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=28 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nOn July 2019, Guilherme comes back to Yeni Malatyaspor on a two seasons\u2013long deal.\n\n==Style of Play==\nGuilherme plays in an offensive midfielder and prefers to play in the middle position.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gale fica mais um ano|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/gale-fica-mais-um-ano|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=6 June 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: \"Conquistar trof\u00e9u \u00e9 um dos objetivos\"|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-conquistar-trofeu-e-um-dos-objetivos-467645|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=11 October 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Goal.com said about Guilherme, commenting: \"he\u2019s a Brazilian of great creativity and imagination, able to make himself valuable for his team with a play of class or a winning assist for his teammate\".<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\"/>\n\nDuring at his early career at Legia Warsaw, Guilherme also played in the left\u2013back position, reflecting: \"At this point I focus on the left defense, because I'm needed there. Therefore, I listen to many comments, watch matches, analyzing the players' play in this position. For sure, the fact that I'm doing so well on left defense is caused by the help of the training staff. There really was no conversation with the trainer about the game on the left defense.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-gra-dla-takich-kibicow-to-zaszczyt-45189|title=GUILHERME: GRA DLA TAKICH KIBIC\u00d3W TO ZASZCZYT|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131950/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-gra-dla-takich-kibicow-to-zaszczyt-45189|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: Nasz cel to powr\u00f3t na miejsce, na kt\u00f3re zas\u0142ugujemy. Czyli pierwsze|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-nasz-cel-to-powrot-na-miejsce-na-ktore-zaslugujemy-czyli-pierwsze/ar/11298033|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=31 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n{{updated|20 May 2018.}}<ref>{{Soccerway|guilherme-costa-marques/113170}}</ref><ref>{{90minut|26824}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!rowspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[UEFA|Europe]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other<sup>[[#notes gs1|1]]</sup>\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n|[[2009\u201310 Primeira Liga|2009\u201310]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Primeira Liga]]\n|0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Primeira Liga|2010\u201311]]\n|5||1||3||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||8||2\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Primeira Liga|2011\u201312]]\n|0||0||0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!5!!1!!4!!1!!1!!0!!0!!0!!10!!2\n|-\n|[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] (loan)\n|[[2011\u201312 Primeira Liga|2011\u201312]]\n|[[Primeira Liga]]\n|19||0||7||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||26||1\n|-\n|[[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]] (loan)\n|[[2012\u201313 Segunda Liga|2012\u201313]]\n|[[Segunda Liga]]\n|27||4||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||27||4\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|[[Legia Warsaw]]\n|[[2013\u201314 Ekstraklasa|2013\u201314]]\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Ekstraklasa]]\n|2||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Ekstraklasa|2014\u201315]]\n|18||1||6||0||6||0||0||0||30||1\n|-\n|[[2015\u201316 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]]\n|35||5||7||1||12||2||1||0||55||8\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 Ekstraklasa|2016\u201317]]\n|29||5||0||0||11||1||1||1||41||7\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Ekstraklasa|2017\u201318]]\n|15||3||1||0||5||2||1||0||22||5\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!99!!14!!14!!1!!34!!5!!3!!1!!150!!21\n|-\n|[[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]]\n|[[2017\u201318 Serie A|2017\u201318]]\n|[[Serie A]]\n|12||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||12||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!162!!21!!25!!3!!35!!5!!3!!1!!225!!30\n|}\n<span id=\"notes gs1\"></span><sup>1</sup><small> Including [[Polish SuperCup]].</small>\n\n==Personal life==\nGuilherme mentioned in an interview with Gol 24 that he has a wife, implying that he's married. During the same interview, he's currently learning Polish and spoke English and occasionally Portuguese when he was at Legia Warsaw.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme dla Ekstraklasa.net: Legia ma tak samo dobrych pi\u0142karzy, jak Braga|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-dla-ekstraklasanet-legia-ma-tak-samo-dobrych-pilkarzy-jak-braga/ar/9569908|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=4 April 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Having spent four years in Poland, he applied for the [[Poland|Pol]]ish Citizenship to help the club reduce the limit of foreigners in the league.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme ubiega si\u0119 o polskie obywatelstwo. \"Przepis o dw\u00f3ch obcokrajowcach ogranicza kluby\"|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-ubiega-sie-o-polskie-obywatelstwo-przepis-o-dwoch-obcokrajowcach-ogranicza-kluby/ar/11813840|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=21 February 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> In February 2018, Guilherme became a first time father.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: Dla dziecka mog\u0119 zosta\u0107 w Legii|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/guilherme-dla-dziecka-moge-zostac-w-legii/nx4y85b|publisher=Fakt|language=Polish|date=27 November 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nGrowing up in [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil, Guilherme revealed that he stayed all day on the pitch that \"sometime his mother came for me because I forgot about the dinner\".<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Although he described his mother as \"strict\", due to the fact that \"she did not always like that him spending so much time playing football\" and \"demanding\", she, nevertheless, supported him.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> He also grew up supporting [[Clube de Regatas do Flamengo|Flamengo]].<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> He also have a tattoo that said: \"Minha Fam\u00edlia \u00e9 minha vida\" (translated \"My family is my life\") in his right arm.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/prawda-czasu-tatuaze-51549|title=PRAWDA CZASU: TATUA\u017bE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=4 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174657/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/prawda-czasu-tatuaze-51549|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme also has a brother.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nic-nie-jest-w-stanie-mnie-zdekoncentrowac-55396|title=GUILHERME: NIC NIE JEST W STANIE MNIE ZDEKONCENTROWA\u0106|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 May 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126232658/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nic-nie-jest-w-stanie-mnie-zdekoncentrowac-55396|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n\n=== Club ===\n\n;Legia Warsaw\n*[[Ekstraklasa]]: [[2013-14 Ekstraklasa|2013\u201314]], [[2015-16 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 Ekstraklasa|2016\u201317]], [[2017\u201318 Ekstraklasa|2017\u201318]]\n*[[Polish Cup]]: [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Polish Cup|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 Polish Cup|2017\u201318]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|guilherme-costa-marques/113170}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143300/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899 Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente]\n* {{ForaDeJogo}}\n* {{90minut|26824}}\n\n{{Trabzonspor squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Guilherme Costa Marques}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Primeira Liga players]]\n[[Category:Ekstraklasa players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:S.C. Braga players]]\n[[Category:S.C. Braga B players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Vizela players]]\n[[Category:Gil Vicente F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Legia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Benevento Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Yeni Malatyaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Trabzonspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Poland]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Portugal]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Poland]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Italy]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Guilherme\n| fullname = Guilherme Costa Marques\n| image = Met-legia (6).jpg\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1991|5|21|mf=yes}} \n| birth_place = [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil\n| height = {{height|meters=1.74}}\n| currentclub  = [[Trabzonspor]]<br/>(on loan from [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]])\n| clubnumber = 6\n| position = [[Midfielder (football)|Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 = 2008\u20132009\n| youthclubs1 = [[Para\u00edba do Sul Futebol Clube|Para\u00edba do Sul]]\n| youthyears2 = 2009\u20132010\n| youthclubs2 = [[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n| years1 = 2010\u20132015\n| years2 = 2010\u20132011\n| years3 = 2011\u20132012\n| years4 = 2012\u20132013\n| years5 = 2013\u20132015\n| years6 = 2015\u20132018\n| years7 = 2018\u2013\n| years8 = 2018\u20132019\n| years9 = 2019\u20132020\n| years10 = 2020\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n| clubs2 = \u2192 [[F.C. Vizela|Vizela]] (loan)\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] (loan)\n| clubs4 = [[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]]\n| clubs5 = \u2192 [[Legia Warsaw]] (loan)\n| clubs6 = [[Legia Warsaw]]\n| clubs7 = [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]]\n| clubs8 = \u2192 [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] (loan)\n| clubs9 = \u2192 [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] (loan)\n| clubs10 = \u2192 [[Trabzonspor]] (loan)\n| caps1 = 5\n| caps2 = 7\n| caps3 = 19\n| caps4 = 27\n| caps5 = 8\n| caps6 = 91\n| caps7 = 12\n| caps8 = 30\n| caps9 = 18\n| caps10 = 0\n| goals1 = 1\n| goals2 = 0\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 4\n| goals5 = 0\n| goals6 = 14\n| goals7 = 2\n| goals8 = 5\n| goals9 = 5\n| goals10 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| club-update = 18 December 2019\n| ntupdate =\n}}\n\n'''Guilherme Costa Marques''' known as '''Guilherme''' (born May 21, 1991) is a [[Brazil]]ian footballer who plays for Turkish club [[Trabzonspor]] on loan from [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]].\n\n==Club career==\n===SC Braga===\nBorn in [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil,<ref>{{cite news|title=Refor\u00e7o Guilherme agrada a Domingos|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/reforco-guilherme-agrada-a-domingos-593976|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=14 December 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme began playing futsal and trained at a football school.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\">{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-moje-motto-nigdy-sie-nie-poddawaj-49233|title=GUILHERME: MOJE MOTTO? NIGDY SI\u0118 NIE PODDAWAJ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 December 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126160436/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-moje-motto-nigdy-sie-nie-poddawaj-49233 |archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> As he grew older, began to take football seriously.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Guilherme then started out his career at [[Para\u00edba do Sul Futebol Clube|Para\u00edba do Sul]] before moving to Portugal, where he joined [[S.C. Braga|Braga]] in 2009 at age sixteen.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ojago\">{{cite news|title=Todo-o-terreno criativo e com alma guerreira|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/arquivo/2010/03/interior/todo-o-terreno-criativo-e-com-alma-guerreira-2562701.html|publisher=O Jogo|language=Portuguese|date=5 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Jean descartado|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/jean-descartado|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=18 September 2009|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final\"/> Immediately after joining the club, Guilherme was assigned to the youth team.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ojago\"/>\n\nIt wasn't until on 24 January 2010 when he made his SC Braga first team debut, starting the whole game, in a 4\u20131 win over [[U.D. Leiria|Leiria]].<ref>{{cite news|title=BRAGA GOLEIA LEIRIA POR 4-1 NO ADEUS \u00c0 PROVA|url=https://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/taca-da-liga/artigos/braga-goleia-leiria-por-4-1-no-adeus-a-prova|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=24 January 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He also appeared as an unused substitute bench in a league match against [[Vit\u00f3ria F.C.|Vit\u00f3ria]] on 6 March 2010.<ref>{{cite news|title=V. Set\u00fabal-Sp. Braga, 0-0 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/v-setubal-sp-braga-0-0-cronica|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=6 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> For the remaining part of the 2009\u201310 season, Guilherme appeared in a number of matches as an unused substitute bench, as he made one appearance for the side.<ref>{{cite news|title=Miguel Garcia e Diogo Valente reintegrados|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/miguel-garcia-e-diogo-valente-reintegrados|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 March 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Solignac \u00e9 para ficar|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/solignac-e-para-ficar|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=29 April 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nAhead of the 2010\u201311 season, Guilherme was promoted to Braga's senior squad.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gale fica mais um ano|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/gale-fica-mais-um-ano|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=6 June 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> His first appearance of the season came on 21 August 2010, where he came on as a second\u2013half substitute, in a 0\u20130 draw against Vit\u00f3ria.<ref>{{cite news|title=V. Set\u00fabal-Sp. Braga, 0-0 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/sporting-braga-liga-vitoria-setubal-v-setubal-sp-braga-cronica-jornada-2-maisfutebol/520b8a6a3004bc615fd26e79.html|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=21 August 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> It wasn't until on 22 January 2011 when Guilherme scored his first goal of the season, in a 2\u20132 draw against Vit\u00f3ria.<ref>{{cite news|title=Domingos lamenta empate \"injusto\"|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/domingos-lamenta-empate-injusto-68062|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=22 January 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Eight days later, on 30 January 2011, he scored again in the [[2010\u201311 Ta\u00e7a da Liga#Third round|third round of Ta\u00e7a da Liga]], in a 4\u20130 win over [[F.C. Arouca|Arouca]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Ta\u00e7a da Liga: Arouca-Sp.Braga, 0-4 (cr\u00f3nica)|url=https://maisfutebol.iol.pt/taca-da-liga-arouca-sp-braga-0-4-cronica|publisher=Mais Futebol|language=Portuguese|date=30 January 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2010\u201311 season, Guilherme went on to make eight appearances and scoring once in all competitions. During the season, he was linked a move away from SC Braga, as [[Juventus FC|Juventus]], [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]] and [[FC Barcelona]] were interested in signing him.<ref>{{cite news|title=Juventus quer Guilherme (SC Braga) no final da \u00e9poca|url=https://zerozero.co.mz/news.php?id=37020&redird=1|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=17 October 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Juventus avan\u00e7a para Guilherme|url=https://www.record.pt/internacional/detalhe/juventus-avanca-para-guilherme-721955|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=17 October 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nThe start of 2011\u201312 season saw Guilherme making one appearance, which came on 25 August 2011, where he set up a goal for [[Lima (footballer)|Lima]] in a 2\u20132 draw against [[BSC Young Boys]] in the second leg of the UEFA Qualification Play\u2013Off and saw the club go through to the Group Stage, thanks to away goal.<ref>{{cite news|title=QUALIFICA\u00c7\u00c3O FELIZ COM \"SOFRIMENTO\" \u00c0 MISTURA|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/liga-europa/artigos/qualificacao-feliz-com-sofrimento-a-mistura|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=25 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After spending the 2011\u201312 season on loan at Gil Vicente, Guilherme was sent to the [[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]] team for the whole 2012\u201313 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Arranque com cinco caras novas|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/arranque-com-cinco-caras-novas-765360|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 July 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At Braga B team, Guilherme received a handful of playing time despite being called up from the senior team.<ref>{{cite news|title=Peseiro chama An\u00edbal e Guilherme|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/braga/noticias/interior/peseiro-chama-anibal-e-guilherme-2838715.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=20 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Convocat\u00f3ria com Haas|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/1a-liga/braga/noticias/interior/convocatoria-com-haas-2851796.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=27 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=A oportunidade dos jovens|url=https://www.record.pt/opiniao/cronistas/antonio-oliveira/detalhe/a-oportunidade-dos-jovens-796876|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=3 January 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He also helped the side reach the final of [[2012 Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final|final]] against [[S.L. Benfica]], which they lost 2\u20131.<ref name=\"Guilherme Ta\u00e7a da Liga Final\">{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-mam-nature-wojownika-39238|title=GUILHERME: MAM NATUR\u0118 WOJOWNIKA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122211025/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-mam-nature-wojownika-39238|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sent\u2013off on two occasions,<ref>{{cite news|title=Tondela-Braga B, 2-1: Piojo operou reviravolta|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/tondela-braga-b-2-1-piojo-operou-reviravolta-776408|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=2 September 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Penafiel-Sp. Braga B, 2-0: Ferreira e Robson resolvem|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/penafiel-sp-braga-b-2-0-ferreira-e-robson-resolvem-781878|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=7 October 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme went on to make twenty\u2013six appearances and scoring four times for Braga B team.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sp. Braga B-U. Madeira, 1-1: Minhotos continuam sem vencer|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/sp-braga-b-u-madeira-1-1-minhotos-continuam-sem-vencer-775186|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=26 August 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Leix\u00f5es-Sp. Braga B, 1-1: Jovem Kizito salva anfitri\u00f5es|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/leixoes-sp-braga-b-1-1-jovem-kizito-salva-anfitrioes-779644|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=23 September 2012|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Braga B j\u00e1 v\u00ea a salva\u00e7\u00e3o|url=https://www.ojogo.pt/futebol/2a-liga/noticias/interior/braga-b-ja-ve-a-salvacao-3163274.html|publisher=Ojogo|language=Portuguese|date=12 April 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nIt was announced on 19 June 2013 that Guilherme's future at the SC Braga was in doubt, leading the club become more interested in signing him.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme roda outra vez|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-roda-outra-vez-828276|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=19 June 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Canarinhos querem Guilherme emprestado|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/estoril/detalhe/canarinhos-querem-guilherme-emprestado-828535|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=20 June 2013|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He spent the rest of the year, training for the reserve side.<ref name=\"Guilherme 2013\">{{cite news|title=Guilherme w Legii. Wolny zawodnik, a jednak wypo\u017cyczony [KOMENTARZ]|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-w-legii-wolny-zawodnik-a-jednak-wypozyczony-komentarz/ar/9577996|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=15 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> It was announced on 10 January 2014 that Guilherme was expected to leave SC Braga, either having his contract terminated or on loan.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme e Lu\u00eds Alberto despedem-se do SC Braga|url=https://zerozero.co.mz/news.php?id=131189|publisher=Zero Zero|language=Portuguese|date=10 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n====Loan Spells====\nIn the first part of the following season, Guilherme was loaned to [[LigaPro|Segunda Liga]] side [[F.C. Vizela|Vizela]], where he made seven appearances for the side.<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\">{{cite news|title=Calciomercato Benevento, chi \u00e8 Guilherme: estro e fantasia|url=https://www.goal.com/it/notizie/calciomercato-benevento-chi-e-guilherme-estro-e-fantasia/rb7vusy46ni518lbodls2ib9r|publisher=Goal.com|language=Italian|date=11 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nFor the 2011\u201312 season, Guilherme was loaned out to [[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] for the rest of the season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-cedido-ao-gil-vicente-714899|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=31 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899|title=Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente|publisher=Record XL|language=Portuguese|date=31 August 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143300/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme made his Gil Vicente debut on 16 September 2011, where he came on as a second-half substitute, in a 2\u20132 draw against [[S.C. Olhanense|Olhanense]].<ref>{{cite news|title=GIL EMPATA NOS MINUTOS FINAIS|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/primeira-liga/artigos/gil-empata-nos-minutos-finais|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=16 September 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> The following month, on 27 October 2011 in the Ta\u00e7a da Liga campaign, he scored his first goal for Gil Vicente, scoring from a penalty, in a 2\u20131 loss against [[C.F. Os Belenenses|Belenenses]].<ref>{{cite news|title=BELENENSES VENCE GIL VICENTE COM PEN\u00c1LTI TARDIO|url=https://desporto.sapo.ao/futebol/taca-da-liga/artigos/belenenses-vence-gil-vicente-com-penalti-tardio|publisher=Sapo Desporto|language=Portuguese|date=27 October 2011|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Throughout the 2011-2012 season, Guilherme went on to make twenty\u2013six appearances and scoring once in all competitions.\n\n===Legia Warsaw===\nOn 14 January 2014, it was announced that Guilherme was loaned out to [[Legia Warsaw]] for the next twelve months.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-trafi-do-legii-39220|title=GUILHERME TRAFI DO LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=13 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119151109/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-trafi-do-legii-39220|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-podpisal-kontrakt-hd-39239|title=GUILHERME PODPISA\u0141 KONTRAKT (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043157/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-podpisal-kontrakt-hd-39239|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme 2013\"/> Upon joining the club, Guilherme became the twelve [[Brazil]]ian player to join Legia Warsaw.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dwunasty-brazylijczyk-w-legii-39243|title=DWUNASTY BRAZYLIJCZYK W LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 January 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122211011/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dwunasty-brazylijczyk-w-legii-39243|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Legia Warsaw debut on 14 February 2014, where he started the match before being substituted in the 74th minutes, in a 1\u20130 win over [[Korona Kielce]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Znamy sk\u0142ady na mecz Legia - Korona. Debiut Guilherme i Chi\u017cniczenki!|url=https://gol24.pl/znamy-sklady-na-mecz-legia-korona-debiut-guilherme-i-chizniczenki/ar/9575666|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=15 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After making another appearance, he, however, suffered a ruptured intraarticular ligament initiation in the ankle that saw sidelined until the end of the 2013\u201314 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme kontuzjowany na treningu|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-kontuzjowany-na-treningu/ar/9574516|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=25 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme nie zagra przez cztery tygodnie|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-nie-zagra-przez-cztery-tygodnie/ar/9574230|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=28 February 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia nie wyda miliona na Guilherme|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-nie-wyda-miliona-na-guilherme/pf39v66|publisher=Fakt|language=Polish|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> By the time he suffered an ruptured his ankle, Guilherme went on to make two appearances for the side this season. Despite this, he went on to win February's Player of the Month by the club's supporters.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://legia.com/news,40111-guilherme_pilkarzem_miesiaca.html|title=Guilherme pi\u0142karzem miesi\u0105ca|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 March 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016113321/https://legia.com/news,40111-guilherme_pilkarzem_miesiaca.html|archivedate=16 October 2014|url-status=live}}</ref> During his injury, the club went on to win the league.\n\nAt the start of the 2014\u201315 season, Guilherme remained sidelined from the first team, due to suffering from injury.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-w-rzymie-kadrowicze-wracaja-do-zdrowia-43459|title=GUILHERME W RZYMIE, KADROWICZE WRACAJ\u0104 DO ZDROWIA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 September 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122215515/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-w-rzymie-kadrowicze-wracaja-do-zdrowia-43459|archivedate=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> It wasn't until on 17 October 2014 when he made his return from injury, coming on as a substitute, where Legia Warsaw beat [[Lechia Gda\u0144sk]] 1\u20130.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/instynkt-s-n-ajpera-legia-lechia-1-0-44248|title=INSTYNKT S(N)AJPERA. LEGIA - LECHIA 1:0!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=17 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126123623/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/instynkt-s-n-ajpera-legia-lechia-1-0-44248|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/powrot-guilherme-po-238-dniach-44254|title=POWR\u00d3T GUILHERME PO 238 DNIACH|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=18 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126123621/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/powrot-guilherme-po-238-dniach-44254|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Four days later, on 22 October 2014, he made his first start as a left\u2013back since returning from injury, in a 1\u20130 win over [[FC Metalist Kharkiv|Metalist Kharkiv]] in the group stage of the UEFA Europa League.<ref>{{cite news|title=Europa League: Legia Warsaw continue fine form with win over Metalist Kharkiv|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9529454/europa-league-metalist-kharkiv-0-legia-warsaw-1|publisher=Sky Sports|date=22 October 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Since returning to the first team from injury, Guilherme regained his first team place, playing in the left\u2013back position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-legia-zagra-w-belgii-na-luzie-44781|title=DZIENNIKARZE: LEGIA ZAGRA W BELGII NA LUZIE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 November 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131029/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-legia-zagra-w-belgii-na-luzie-44781|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-awansujemy-z-1-miejsca-44997|title=DZIENNIKARZE: AWANSUJEMY Z 1. MIEJSCA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=11 December 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131736/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/dziennikarze-awansujemy-z-1-miejsca-44997|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/brzyski-czy-guilherme-zacieta-walka-na-lewej-obronie-45591|title=BRZYSKI CZY GUILHERME? ZACI\u0118TA WALKA NA LEWEJ OBRONIE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=9 February 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126132149/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/brzyski-czy-guilherme-zacieta-walka-na-lewej-obronie-45591|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The following month on 14 January 2015, it was announced that Guilherme signed for Legia Warsaw on a permanent basis, signing a three\u2013year contract.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme wykupiony, kontrakt na 3,5 roku|url=https://www.onet.pl/?srcc=ucs&pid=58255111-be50-5d50-8ee3-bf6dc6133366&sid=4390aa51-c69b-410e-bc0a-a3c3c7c23e1d|publisher=Onet.pl|language=Polish|date=14 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-na-dluzej-w-legii-45457|title=GUILHERME NA D\u0141U\u017bEJ W LEGII!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=30 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131939/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-na-dluzej-w-legii-45457|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After losing his place by the returning [[Tomasz Brzyski]], Guilherme regained his first team place in attacking position, although he occasionally played at the left\u2013back position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-wisla-46038|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z WIS\u0141\u0104?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=15 March 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126135606/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-wisla-46038|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/berg-presja-jest-z-nami-zawsze-hd-46251|title=BERG: PRESJA JEST Z NAMI ZAWSZE (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=3 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126140028/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/berg-presja-jest-z-nami-zawsze-hd-46251|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-najwazniejsze-zeby-legia-osiagala-swoje-cele-hd-46252|title=GUILHERME: NAJWA\u017bNIEJSZE, \u017bEBY LEGIA OSI\u0104GA\u0141A SWOJE CELE (HD)|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=3 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126140030/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-najwazniejsze-zeby-legia-osiagala-swoje-cele-hd-46252|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His first goal for the club came on 29 April 2015, where he scored an equaliser, in a 2\u20131 win over [[Pogo\u0144 Szczecin]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia przegrywa\u0142a, ale ogra\u0142a Pogo\u0144. Mistrz Polski liderem po podziale punkt\u00f3w|url=https://gol24.pl/legia-przegrywala-ale-ograla-pogon-mistrz-polski-liderem-po-podziale-punktow/ar/9525284|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=29 April 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Three days later, on 2 May 2015, Guilherme helped the beat [[Lech Pozna\u0144]], who went on to win the league, 2\u20131 in the [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup#Final|Polish Cup]] final.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/lech-legia-1-2-puchar-jest-nasz-46595|title=LECH - LEGIA 1:2. PUCHAR JEST NASZ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=2 May 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126141256/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/lech-legia-1-2-puchar-jest-nasz-46595|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/tytul-nie-dla-legii-zabraklo-jednego-punktu-47035|title=TYTU\u0141 NIE DLA LEGII. ZABRAK\u0141O JEDNEGO PUNKTU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 June 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142959/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/tytul-nie-dla-legii-zabraklo-jednego-punktu-47035|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sidelined several times later in the 2014\u201315 season,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-ruchem-44484|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z RUCHEM?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=2 November 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126130618/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-ruchem-44484|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-podbeskidziem-45877|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z PODBESKIDZIEM?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 March 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126134500/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-podbeskidziem-45877|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-pogonia-46858|title=JAKIM SK\u0141ADEM Z POGONI\u0104?|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=23 May 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142459/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/jakim-skladem-z-pogonia-46858|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme went on to make thirty appearances and scoring once for the side.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/podsumowujemy-sezon-wystepy-minuty-47051|title=PODSUMOWUJEMY SEZON: WYST\u0118PY/MINUTY|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=9 June 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126142943/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/podsumowujemy-sezon-wystepy-minuty-47051|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAt the start of the 2015\u201316 season, Guilherme remained in the first team regular for the side, where he played in the right\u2013wing position despite competing with [[Micha\u0142 Kucharczyk]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-prasie-po-klasyku-47771|title=W PRASIE PO KLASYKU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=10 August 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126150450/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-prasie-po-klasyku-47771|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|title=Guilherme: Plotki o zmianie trenera nie mia\u0142y na nas wp\u0142ywu|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-plotki-o-zmianie-trenera-nie-mialy-na-nas-wplywu/ar/9508176|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=2 October 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-wszyscy-pracujemy-na-sukces-naszej-legii-49427|title=GUILHERME: WSZYSCY PRACUJEMY NA SUKCES NASZEJ LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=10 December 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126162614/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-wszyscy-pracujemy-na-sukces-naszej-legii-49427|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He started the season well when he scored in the second leg of the UEFA Europa League Qualification against [[FC Boto\u0219ani]], in a 3\u20130 win to advance to the next round.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/botosani-legia-0-3-wojskowi-w-iii-rundzie-47553|title=BOTOSANI - LEGIA 0:3. 'WOJSKOWI' W III RUNDZIE!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=23 July 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126145259/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/botosani-legia-0-3-wojskowi-w-iii-rundzie-47553|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> A month later, on 27 August 2015, Guilherme scored again in the play\u2013offs round of the UEFA Europa League, in a 3\u20132 win over [[FC Zorya Luhansk|Zorya Luhansk]] to advance to the Group Stage.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legionisci-o-meczu-z-zoria-48025|title=LEGIONI\u015aCI O MECZU Z ZORI\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 August 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126153224/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legionisci-o-meczu-z-zoria-48025|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Three days later, on 30 August 2015, he scored his first league goal of the season, in a 1\u20131 draw against [[Jagiellonia Bia\u0142ystok]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/1-1-w-bialymstoku-remis-w-ostatnim-meczu-przed-przerwa-48068|title=1:1 W BIA\u0141YMSTOKU. REMIS W OSTATNIM MECZU PRZED PRZERW\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=30 August 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126153646/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/1-1-w-bialymstoku-remis-w-ostatnim-meczu-przed-przerwa-48068|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His performance at Legia Warsaw attracted interests from Serie A side [[Inter Milan]], but the move never happened.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme na celowniku Interu Mediolan!|url=http://sportowefakty.wp.pl/pilka-nozna/558360/guilherme-na-celowniku-interu-mediolan|publisher=Sportowe Fakty|language=Polish|date=5 November 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After being sidelined on two separate matches between late\u2013February and early\u2013March,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-kucharczyka-i-guilherme-z-ruchem-50430|title=BEZ KUCHARCZYKA I GUILHERME Z RUCHEM|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=21 February 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126170411/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-kucharczyka-i-guilherme-z-ruchem-50430|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-wraca-na-zwycieska-sciezke-50684|title=LEGIA WRACA NA ZWYCI\u0118SK\u0104 \u015aCIE\u017bK\u0118!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 March 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126171013/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-wraca-na-zwycieska-sciezke-50684|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme scored on his return from the sidelined on 12 March 2016, in a 2\u20131 win over [[KS Cracovia (football)|KS Cracovia]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-warszawa-wciaz-na-tronie-50799|title=LEGIA WARSZAWA WCI\u0104\u017b NA TRONIE!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 March 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126171554/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-warszawa-wciaz-na-tronie-50799|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> The following month, he scored the second leg of the semi\u2013final of the Polish Cup, in a 2\u20131 win over [[Zawisza Bydgoszcz]] to reach the final; which they beat Lech Pozna\u0144 again in the [[2015\u201316 Polish Cup#Final|Polish Cup]] final for the second time in a row.<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia Warsaw dope\u0142ni\u0142a formalno\u015bci|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-dopelnila-formalnosci/9qt9ez3|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=6 April 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Fina\u0142 Pucharu Polski: Legia Warszawa lepsza od Lecha Pozna\u0144. Skandal na trybunach|url=https://www.newsweek.pl/sport/final-pucharu-polski-2016-legia-warszawa-lech-poznan-bramki/hde35st|publisher=Newsweek Polska|language=Polish|date=2 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After adding his eighth goal of the season against [[Piast Gliwice]] on 8 May 2016, Guilherme helped the side win the league.<ref>{{cite news|title=Deklasacja w Warszawie. Znamy mistrza Polski?|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/legia-warszawa-piast-gliwice-40-legia-jest-juz-blisko-mistrzostwa-polski-jesli-w/8s1q3qm#slajd-1|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=8 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia Warszawa mistrzem Polski!|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/ekstraklasa-legia-warszawa-pogon-szczecin-gra-o-mistrzostwo-polski-relacja-live-na/eezdvf0|publisher=Fakt 24|language=Polish|date=15 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2015\u201316 season, he went on to make 55 appearances and scoring 8 times in all competitions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-to-jest-legia-presja-to-norma-51763|title=GUILHERME: TO JEST LEGIA, PRESJA TO NORMA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=20 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174623/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-to-jest-legia-presja-to-norma-51763|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAt the start of the 2016\u201317 season, Guilherme started the season when he scored the club's first goal of the season, as Legia Warrsaw lost 4\u20131 to Lech Pozna\u0144 in the [[2016 Polish SuperCup|Polish SuperCup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przegrana-legii-w-meczu-o-superpuchar-52355|title=PRZEGRANA LEGII W MECZU O SUPERPUCHAR|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126195745/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przegrana-legii-w-meczu-o-superpuchar-52355|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> But he soon suffered a shoulder injury during a 2\u20130 win over [[H\u0160K Zrinjski Mostar|Zrinjski Mostar]] in the second leg of the UEFA Champions League second round and was sidelined for a month.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme czeka operacja i d\u0142uga przerwa w grze|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-czeka-operacja-i-dluga-przerwa-w-grze/ar/10430060|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=21 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Kontuzja barku Guilherme. \"Pozostaje modli\u0107 si\u0119, by to nie by\u0142o nic powa\u017cnego\"|url=https://gol24.pl/kontuzja-barku-guilherme-pozostaje-modlic-sie-by-to-nie-bylo-nic-powaznego/ar/10426080|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=20 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> He then made his return from injury on 20 August 2016 against [[Arka Gdynia]], where he came on as a second-half substitute and set up a goal for [[Kasper H\u00e4m\u00e4l\u00e4inen]], in a 3\u20131 loss.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-arka-1-3-52914|title=LEGIA WARSAW - ARKA GDYNIA 1: 3|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=20 August 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126201834/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-arka-1-3-52914|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Since returning from a shoulder injury, Guilherme regained his first team place, playing in the right\u2013wing position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-bedzie-coraz-lepiej-52445|title=GUILHERME: B\u0118DZIE CORAZ LEPIEJ!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 July 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126195734/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-bedzie-coraz-lepiej-52445|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite news|title=Legia Warszawa \u2013 Lech Pozna\u0144. Nenad Bjelica: Kogo chcia\u0142bym wykupi\u0107 z Legii? Nikogo|url=http://poznan.wyborcza.pl/poznan/1,36006,20873218,legia-warszawa-lech-poznan-nenad-bjelica-kogo-chcialbym.html|publisher=Wyborcza Poznan|language=Polish|date=22 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 1 October 2016, Guilherme scored a brace, scoring from the first and second goal of the game, in a 3\u20130 win over [[Lechia Gda\u0144sk]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przebudzenie-mistrzow-53417|title=PRZEBUDZENIE MISTRZ\u00d3W|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126204204/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/przebudzenie-mistrzow-53417|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Then, on 7 December 2016, he scored his first UEFA Champions League goal, in a 1\u20130 win over [[Sporting CP]], their first win of the UEFA Champions League's Group Stage.<ref>{{cite news|title=Mecz Legia \u2013 Sporting. Waleczna Legia pokona\u0142a Sporting! Jest trzecie miejsce i Liga Europy|url=https://gol24.pl/mecz-legia-sporting-waleczna-legia-pokonala-sporting-jest-trzecie-miejsce-i-liga-europy/ar/11553310|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=7 December 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> The following month saw the club opened a contract negotiation to convince Guilherme stay at the club beyond 2018, whose contract was expected to expire.<ref>{{cite news|title=Legia straci Guilherme?|url=https://gol24.pl/legia-straci-guilherme/ar/11660040|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=5 January 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Later in the 2016\u201317 season, he helped the club win the league for the second time in a row on the last game of the season.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mniej-biegania-wiecej-taktyki-55281|title=MNIEJ BIEGANIA, WI\u0118CEJ TAKTYKI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=26 April 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126230915/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mniej-biegania-wiecej-taktyki-55281|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzem-polski-jest-legia-55566|title=MISTRZEM POLSKI JEST LEGIA!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=5 June 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126223721/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzem-polski-jest-legia-55566|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Despite being sidelined later in the 2016\u201317 season,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-radovicia-i-guilherme-z-wisla-54069|title=BEZ RADOVICIA I GUILHERME Z WIS\u0141\u0104|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=28 November 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126224900/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/bez-radovicia-i-guilherme-z-wisla-54069|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-w-czwartkowej-prasie-i-mediach-54102|title=LEGIA W CZWARTKOWEJ PRASIE I MEDIACH|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 December 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126224909/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-w-czwartkowej-prasie-i-mediach-54102|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-korona-ciekawostki-55211|title=LEGIA - KORONA: CIEKAWOSTKI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 April 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126230904/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/legia-korona-ciekawostki-55211|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> he went on to make 41 appearances and scoring 7 times in all competitions.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzowie-z-l3-oni-zdobyli-tytul-55542|title=MISTRZOWIE Z \u01413 - ONI ZDOBYLI TYTU\u0141|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=4 June 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126232429/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/mistrzowie-z-l3-oni-zdobyli-tytul-55542|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nAhead of the 2017\u201318 season, Guilherme was linked away from the club, as Sporting CP and [[Trabzonspor]] were among interested.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sporting Lizbona zg\u0142asza si\u0119 po pi\u0142karza Legii|url=https://gol24.pl/sporting-lizbona-zglasza-sie-po-pilkarza-legii/ar/12063616|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=10 May 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Wyprzeda\u017c w Legii? Guilherme na celowniku Trabzonsporu|url=https://gol24.pl/wyprzedaz-w-legii-guilherme-na-celowniku-trabzonsporu/ar/12219891|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=28 June 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Despite this, Guilherme stayed at the club and started the season when he set up the equaliser for [[Thibault Moulin]] to score against Arka Gdynia in the [[2017 Polish SuperCup|Polish SuperCup]] on 7 July 2017; leading the match to extra\u2013time and penalty shoot\u2013out, where he successfully converted the shootout, but lost 4\u20133 in the penalty shoot\u2013out.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zdjac-klatwe-superpucharu-55812|title=ZDJ\u0104\u0106 KL\u0104TW\u0118 SUPERPUCHARU|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=7 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194805/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zdjac-klatwe-superpucharu-55812|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He then scored in both legs of the UEFA Champions League Second Round Qualification against [[IFK Mariehamn]] in a 9\u20130 on aggregate to advance to the next round.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pierwszy-krok-wykonany-55859|title=PIERWSZY KROK WYKONANY!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194743/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pierwszy-krok-wykonany-55859|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pogrom-i-pewny-awans-do-iii-rundy-eliminacji-lm-uefa-55908|title=POGROM I PEWNY AWANS DO III RUNDY ELIMINACJI LM UEFA!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 July 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129194748/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/pogrom-i-pewny-awans-do-iii-rundy-eliminacji-lm-uefa-55908|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> However, Guilherme was sidelined for a month after suffering a knee injury during a 1\u20131 draw against [[FC Sheriff Tiraspol|Sheriff Tiraspol]] in a UEFA Europa League Play\u2013Off Round match in the first leg.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/kilka-tygodni-przerwy-guilherme-56257|title=KILKA TYGODNI PRZERWY GUILHERME|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=19 August 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129203849/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/kilka-tygodni-przerwy-guilherme-56257|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After returning to training, he didn't make his return to the first team on 1 October 2017, coming on as a second-half substitute, in a 3\u20130 loss against Lech Poznan.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/trening-z-guilherme-56513|title=TRENING Z GUILHERME|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=15 September 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129203846/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/trening-z-guilherme-56513|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-poznaniu-na-smutno-56630|title=W POZNANIU NA SMUTNO|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=1 October 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210447/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/w-poznaniu-na-smutno-56630|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme then scored two goals in two matches between on 9 December 2017 and 12 December 2017 against [[Bruk-Bet Termalica Nieciecza]] and [[Piast Gliwice]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Lotto Ekstraklasa. Hamalainen zata\u0144czy\u0142 z Termalik\u0105, G\u00f3rnik poczu\u0142 oddech Legii na plecach|url=https://gol24.pl/lotto-ekstraklasa-hamalainen-zatanczyl-z-termalika-gornik-poczul-oddech-legii-na-plecach/ar/12752647|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=9 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zadanie-wykonane-legia-znowu-liderem-57222|title=ZADANIE WYKONANE, LEGIA ZNOWU LIDEREM!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=12 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210346/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/zadanie-wykonane-legia-znowu-liderem-57222|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> It was announced on 8 December 2017 that Guilherme was not signing a new contract with Legia Warsaw and expected to leave the club when the transfer window opens next month.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-przedluzy-kontraktu-z-legia-warszawa-57190|title=GUILHERME NIE PRZED\u0141U\u017bY KONTRAKTU Z LEGI\u0104 WARSZAWA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=8 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210415/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-przedluzy-kontraktu-z-legia-warszawa-57190|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> His last appearance, which also coincidentally turns out to be his 150th appearance for Legia Warsaw, came on 16 December 2017, in a 2\u20130 loss against [[Wis\u0142a P\u0142ock]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/150-mecz-guilherme-w-legii-57264|title=150. MECZ GUILHERME W LEGII|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210339/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/150-mecz-guilherme-w-legii-57264|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> After the match, he made a farewell statements, thanking the club during his four years spell there.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/gui-dziekujemy-57247|title=GUI \u2013 DZI\u0118KUJEMY!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210336/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/gui-dziekujemy-57247|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-bylo-to-pozegnanie-o-jakim-marzylem-57278|title=GUILHERME: NIE BY\u0141O TO PO\u017bEGNANIE, O JAKIM MARZY\u0141EM|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210334/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nie-bylo-to-pozegnanie-o-jakim-marzylem-57278|archivedate=31 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> By the time he departed the club, Guilherme's contribution to the club winning the league this season, where he made 22 appearances and scoring five times, earned him a medal.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/oni-zdobyli-14-tytul-mistrza-polski-58735|title=ONI ZDOBYLI 14. TYTU\u0141 MISTRZA POLSKI!|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=22 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210328/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/oni-zdobyli-14-tytul-mistrza-polski-58735|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nDuring his time at Legia Warsaw, Guilherme made 150 appearances and scoring 21 times, as he helped the side win the Polish Cup on two occasions and the league on three occasions.<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/najbardziej-utytulowani-legionisci-58861|title=NAJBARDZIEJ UTYTU\u0141OWANI LEGIONI\u015aCI|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 June 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190129210325/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/najbardziej-utytulowani-legionisci-58861|archivedate=29 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> He was also the club's fan favourite, due to his dribbling and shooting skills.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-czyli-pomocnik-z-prawdziwego-zdarzenia-51464|title=GUILHERME, CZYLI POMOCNIK Z PRAWDZIWEGO ZDARZENIA|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=27 April 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174716/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-czyli-pomocnik-z-prawdziwego-zdarzenia-51464|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n===Benevento===\nWith his contract not being renewed, Guilherme was linked a move to [[Serie A]] side [[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]], who was at 20th place at the time, and was looking for reinforcements to help the side avoid relegation.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento, accelerata per Guilherme del Legia Varsavia|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-accelerata-per-guilherme-del-legia-varsavia-1051634|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=8 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Benevento, accordo con Guilherme. De Ceglie continua il provino|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-accordo-con-guilherme-de-ceglie-continua-il-provino-1052959|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=12 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 16 December 2017, Italian media Tutto Mercato Web reported that Guilherme agreed a deal to join the club.<ref>{{cite news|title=ESCLUSIVA TMW - Benevento, l'ag. di Guilherme a Varsavia|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/esclusiva-tmw-benevento-l-ag-di-guilherme-a-varsavia-1054463|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=16 December 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> However, his move to Benevento was delayed over paperwork issues.<ref>{{cite news|title=ESCLUSIVA TMW - Benevento, Guilherme dopo la sosta: documenti da finire|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/esclusiva-tmw-benevento-guilherme-dopo-la-sosta-documenti-da-finire-1061359|publisher=Tutto Mercato|language=Italian|date=5 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Eventually, it was announced on 19 January 2018 that he joined Benevento.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.beneventocalcio.club/news/notizie/910/arrivato-il-transfer-per-guilherme.shtml|title=ARRIVATO IL TRANSFER PER GUILHERME.|publisher=Benevento Calcio|language=Italian|date=19 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190130192758/https://www.beneventocalcio.club/news/notizie/910/arrivato-il-transfer-per-guilherme.shtml|archivedate=30 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Benevento debut on 21 January 2018 against [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna]], where he started the whole game, in a 3\u20130 loss.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bologna-Benevento 3-0: Destro, De Maio e Dzemaili fanno ripartire i rossobl\u00f9|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2018/01/21/news/bologna_batte_benevento-186977409/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=21 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After his making his debut, Eurosport gave his performance 6/10, commenting: \"Encouraging the performance of the last arrived; in the first part of the race he sows panic in the opposing defence.\"<ref>{{cite news|title=Le pagelle di Bologna-Benevento 3-0|url=https://it.eurosport.com/calcio/serie-a/2017-2018/le-pagelle-di-bologna-benevento-3-0_sto6491768/story.shtml|publisher=Eurosport|language=Italian|date=21 January 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> His first goal came on 11 February 2018, in a 5\u20132 loss against [[A.S. Roma|Roma]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Roma-Benevento 5-2: Under doppietta, Di Francesco scavalca la Lazio|url=https://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Serie-A/Roma/11-02-2018/roma-benevento-5-2-doppietta-under-francesco-scavalca-lazio-250216869964.shtml|publisher=La Gazzetta Dello Sport|language=Italian|date=11 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> A month later on 31 March 2018, he scored again, which saw Benevento lost 6\u20132 loss against [[SS Lazio|Lazio]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Lazio-Benevento 6-2: i biancocelesti prima soffrono, poi dilagano|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2018/03/31/news/lazio_batte_benevento-192674613/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=31 March 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> However, Guilherme suffered ankle injury during a 2\u20132 draw against [[U.S. Sassuolo Calcio|Sassuolo]] on 15 April 2018 and was expected to be out for the rest of the season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento, stagione finita per Guilherme|url=https://sport.virgilio.it/benevento-stagione-finita-per-guilherme-40771|publisher=Sport Virgilio|language=Italian|date=16 April 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> While on the sidelined, the club were relegated to Serie B after spending one season at Serie A.<ref>{{cite news|title=Benevento relegated to Serie B|url=https://www.football-italia.net/120310/benevento-relegated-serie-b|publisher=Football Italia|date=22 April 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> But on the last game of the season, he made his return from injury on 20 May 2018 against [[A.C. ChievoVerona|Chievo]], starting the whole game, in a 1\u20130 loss.<ref>{{cite news|title=Chievo-Benevento 1-0: Inglese saluta con il gol salvezza|url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/chievo/2018/05/20/news/chievo-benevento_1-0_festa_gialloblu_inglese_saluta_con_il_gol-196918662/|publisher=La Repubblica|language=Italian|date=20 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> At the end of the 2017\u201318 season, Guilherme went on to make twelve appearances and scoring two times in all competitions.\n\nFollowing the club's relegation, Guilherme was linked a move away from Benevento despite being keen on playing in Serie B next season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Tre club di A si muovono per Guilherme|url=https://sport.virgilio.it/tre-club-di-a-si-muovono-per-guilherme-47238|publisher=Sport Virgilio|language=Italian|date=10 May 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme-Benevento \u00e8 rottura, Foggia: \"Chi non ha motivazioni pu\u00f2 stare a casa\"|url=https://www.anteprima24.it/benevento/guilherme-benevento-rottura/|publisher=Ante Prima|language=Italian|date=5 July 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme zbuntowa\u0142 si\u0119 w Benevento. By\u0142y gracz Legii ma ofert\u0119 z Serie A|url=http://futbol.pl/news/560977_Guilherme_zbuntowal_sie_w_Benevento_Byly_gracz_Legii_ma_oferte_z_Serie_A|publisher=Futbol.pl|language=Polish|date=18 July 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Benevento, Guilherme: \"Non ho problemi a restare anche in B\"|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/benevento-guilherme-non-ho-problemi-a-restare-anche-in-b-1082733|publisher=Tutto Mercato Web|language=Italian|date=28 February 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n====Yeni Malatyaspor (loan)====\nIt was announced on 4 August 2018 that Guilherme joined [[Yeni Malatyaspor]] on a season\u2013long deal for the 2018\u201319 season.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme, Yeni Malatyaspor'da|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/guilherme-yeni-malatyasporda-40918382|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=4 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Guilherme\u2019ye imza attirdi|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/yeni-malatyaspor-guilherme-ye-evkur-yeni-malatyaspor-2718967-skorerhaber/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=4 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nGuilherme made his Yeni Malatyaspor debut in the opening game of the season, where he started the match before being substituted in the 81st minutes, in a 3\u20131 win over [[G\u00f6ztepe S.K.|G\u00f6ztepe]].<ref>{{cite news|title=G\u00f6ztepe - Evkur Malatyaspor: 1-3 (\u00d6ZET)|url=http://tr.beinsports.com/haber/goztepe-evkur-malatyaspor|publisher=Bein Sports|language=Turkish|date=12 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> In a follow up match against [[Fenerbah\u00e7e S.K. (football)|Fenerbah\u00e7e]] seven days later on 19 August 2018, he played a vital role for the side when he set up a goal for [[Danijel Aleksi\u0107]] to score the only goal in the game, in a 1\u20130 victory.<ref>{{cite news|title=Fenerbah\u00e7e gols\u00fcz, puans\u0131z, \u0131\u015f\u0131ks\u0131z!|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/fenerbahce-golsuz-puansiz-isiksiz-40932012|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=19 August 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> On 15 September 2018, Guilherme scored his first goal for the club, in a 2\u20131 loss against [[Be\u015fikta\u015f J.K.|Be\u015fikta\u015f]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Be\u015fikta\u015f 10 ki\u015fiyle kazand\u0131|url=https://www.sabah.com.tr/spor/futbol/2018/09/16/canli-besiktas-evkur-yeni-malatyaspor|publisher=Sabah|language=Turkish|date=16 September 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Then, on 9 November 2018, he scored a brace and set up two of the other three goals, in a 5\u20130 win over [[Trabzonspor]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Trabzonspor farkl\u0131 yenildi|url=https://www.sabah.com.tr/spor/futbol/2018/11/10/trabzonspor-zorlu-deplasmanda|publisher=Sabah|language=Turkish|date=10 November 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Since joining the club, he quickly established himself in the starting eleven and impressed the management with his display.<ref>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor'un \"yenileri\" g\u00f6z dolduruyor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/yeni-malatyasporun-yenileri-goz-dolduruyor-40968321|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=26 September 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Malatyaspor'da Guilherme harekat\u0131 ba\u015flad\u0131!|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/malatyasporda-guilherme-harekati-basladi-41059408|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=21 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: 'Art\u0131k teknoloji futbola girdi. Bu duruma herkesin al\u0131\u015fmas\u0131 gerekiyor'|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/guilherme-artik-teknoloji-futbola-girdi-bu-duruma-herkesin-alismasi-gerekiyor-40977714|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=5 October 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Despite suffering an injury and facing suspension at separate times towards the end of the year,<ref>{{cite news|title=Malatyaspor, Antalyaspor'a haz\u0131rlan\u0131yor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/malatyaspor-antalyaspora-hazirlaniyor-41048549|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=12 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Kas\u0131mpa\u015fa ma\u00e7\u0131na haz\u0131rlan\u0131yor|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/yerel-haberler/malatya/yeni-malatyaspor-kasimpasa-macina-hazirlaniyor-41025291|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=20 November 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme then scored again and was sent\u2013off later in the game, in a 1\u20131 draw against [[Bursaspor]] on 23 December 2018.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bursaspor Yeni Malatya'y\u0131 elinden ka\u00e7\u0131rd\u0131|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/bursaspor-yeni-malatyayi-elinden-kacirdi-41061219|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=23 December 2018|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> After suffering an injury and facing suspension at separate times once again in early\u2013January,<ref>{{cite news|title=\"Sonuna Kadar Tak\u0131m\u0131n Ba\u015f\u0131nda Duraca\u011f\u0131m\"|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/sonuna-kadar-takimin-basinda-duracagim-malatya-yerelhaber-3229067/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=15 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Yeni Malatyaspor, Fenerbah\u00e7e'ye Konuk Olacak|url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/yeni-malatyaspor-fenerbahce-ye-konuk-malatya-yerelhaber-3234926/|publisher=Milliyet|language=Turkish|date=27 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Guilherme made his return to the first team on 28 January 2019, in a 3\u20132 loss against Fenerbah\u00e7e.<ref>{{cite news|title=Fenerbah\u00e7e uykudan uyand\u0131: 3-2|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/fenerbahce-uykusundan-uyandi-41097085|publisher=Hurriyet|language=Turkish|date=28 January 2019|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nOn July 2019, Guilherme comes back to Yeni Malatyaspor on a two seasons\u2013long deal.\n\n==Style of Play==\nGuilherme plays in an offensive midfielder and prefers to play in the middle position.<ref>{{cite news|title=Gale fica mais um ano|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/gale-fica-mais-um-ano|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=6 June 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: \"Conquistar trof\u00e9u \u00e9 um dos objetivos\"|url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/sp--braga/detalhe/guilherme-conquistar-trofeu-e-um-dos-objetivos-467645|publisher=Record|language=Portuguese|date=11 October 2010|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> Goal.com said about Guilherme, commenting: \"he\u2019s a Brazilian of great creativity and imagination, able to make himself valuable for his team with a play of class or a winning assist for his teammate\".<ref name=\"Guilherme FC Vizela\"/>\n\nDuring at his early career at Legia Warsaw, Guilherme also played in the left\u2013back position, reflecting: \"At this point I focus on the left defense, because I'm needed there. Therefore, I listen to many comments, watch matches, analyzing the players' play in this position. For sure, the fact that I'm doing so well on left defense is caused by the help of the training staff. There really was no conversation with the trainer about the game on the left defense.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-gra-dla-takich-kibicow-to-zaszczyt-45189|title=GUILHERME: GRA DLA TAKICH KIBIC\u00d3W TO ZASZCZYT|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=6 January 2015|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126131950/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-gra-dla-takich-kibicow-to-zaszczyt-45189|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}<br>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: Nasz cel to powr\u00f3t na miejsce, na kt\u00f3re zas\u0142ugujemy. Czyli pierwsze|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-nasz-cel-to-powrot-na-miejsce-na-ktore-zaslugujemy-czyli-pierwsze/ar/11298033|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=31 October 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n{{updated|20 May 2018.}}<ref>{{Soccerway|guilherme-costa-marques/113170}}</ref><ref>{{90minut|26824}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!rowspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[UEFA|Europe]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other<sup>[[#notes gs1|1]]</sup>\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n!Apps\n!Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[S.C. Braga|Braga]]\n|[[2009\u201310 Primeira Liga|2009\u201310]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Primeira Liga]]\n|0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Primeira Liga|2010\u201311]]\n|5||1||3||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||8||2\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Primeira Liga|2011\u201312]]\n|0||0||0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!5!!1!!4!!1!!1!!0!!0!!0!!10!!2\n|-\n|[[Gil Vicente F.C.|Gil Vicente]] (loan)\n|[[2011\u201312 Primeira Liga|2011\u201312]]\n|[[Primeira Liga]]\n|19||0||7||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||26||1\n|-\n|[[S.C. Braga B|Braga B]] (loan)\n|[[2012\u201313 Segunda Liga|2012\u201313]]\n|[[Segunda Liga]]\n|27||4||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||27||4\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\"|[[Legia Warsaw]]\n|[[2013\u201314 Ekstraklasa|2013\u201314]]\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[Ekstraklasa]]\n|2||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||2||0\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Ekstraklasa|2014\u201315]]\n|18||1||6||0||6||0||0||0||30||1\n|-\n|[[2015\u201316 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]]\n|35||5||7||1||12||2||1||0||55||8\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 Ekstraklasa|2016\u201317]]\n|29||5||0||0||11||1||1||1||41||7\n|-\n|[[2017\u201318 Ekstraklasa|2017\u201318]]\n|15||3||1||0||5||2||1||0||22||5\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!99!!14!!14!!1!!34!!5!!3!!1!!150!!21\n|-\n|[[Benevento Calcio|Benevento]]\n|[[2017\u201318 Serie A|2017\u201318]]\n|[[Serie A]]\n|12||2||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||12||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!162!!21!!25!!3!!35!!5!!3!!1!!225!!30\n|}\n<span id=\"notes gs1\"></span><sup>1</sup><small> Including [[Polish SuperCup]].</small>\n\n==Personal life==\nGuilherme mentioned in an interview with Gol 24 that he has a wife, implying that he's married. During the same interview, he's currently learning Polish and spoke English and occasionally Portuguese when he was at Legia Warsaw.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme dla Ekstraklasa.net: Legia ma tak samo dobrych pi\u0142karzy, jak Braga|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-dla-ekstraklasanet-legia-ma-tak-samo-dobrych-pilkarzy-jak-braga/ar/9569908|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=4 April 2014|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Having spent four years in Poland, he applied for the [[Poland|Pol]]ish Citizenship to help the club reduce the limit of foreigners in the league.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme ubiega si\u0119 o polskie obywatelstwo. \"Przepis o dw\u00f3ch obcokrajowcach ogranicza kluby\"|url=https://gol24.pl/guilherme-ubiega-sie-o-polskie-obywatelstwo-przepis-o-dwoch-obcokrajowcach-ogranicza-kluby/ar/11813840|publisher=Gol 24|language=Polish|date=21 February 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref> In February 2018, Guilherme became a first time father.<ref>{{cite news|title=Guilherme: Dla dziecka mog\u0119 zosta\u0107 w Legii|url=https://www.fakt.pl/sport/pilka-nozna/guilherme-dla-dziecka-moge-zostac-w-legii/nx4y85b|publisher=Fakt|language=Polish|date=27 November 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nGrowing up in [[Tr\u00eas Rios]], Brazil, Guilherme revealed that he stayed all day on the pitch that \"sometime his mother came for me because I forgot about the dinner\".<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> Although he described his mother as \"strict\", due to the fact that \"she did not always like that him spending so much time playing football\" and \"demanding\", she, nevertheless, supported him.<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> He also grew up supporting [[Clube de Regatas do Flamengo|Flamengo]].<ref name=\"Guilherme Childhood\"/> He also have a tattoo that said: \"Minha Fam\u00edlia \u00e9 minha vida\" (translated \"My family is my life\") in his right arm.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/prawda-czasu-tatuaze-51549|title=PRAWDA CZASU: TATUA\u017bE|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=4 May 2016|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126174657/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/prawda-czasu-tatuaze-51549|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> Guilherme also has a brother.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nic-nie-jest-w-stanie-mnie-zdekoncentrowac-55396|title=GUILHERME: NIC NIE JEST W STANIE MNIE ZDEKONCENTROWA\u0106|publisher=Legia Warsaw|language=Polish|date=14 May 2017|accessdate=31 January 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126232658/http://legia.com/aktualnosci/guilherme-nic-nie-jest-w-stanie-mnie-zdekoncentrowac-55396|archivedate=26 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n\n=== Club ===\n\n;Legia Warsaw\n*[[Ekstraklasa]]: [[2013-14 Ekstraklasa|2013\u201314]], [[2015-16 Ekstraklasa|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 Ekstraklasa|2016\u201317]], [[2017\u201318 Ekstraklasa|2017\u201318]]\n*[[Polish Cup]]: [[2014\u201315 Polish Cup|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 Polish Cup|2015\u201316]], [[2017\u201318 Polish Cup|2017\u201318]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway|guilherme-costa-marques/113170}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143300/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Nacional/1a_liga/sporting_braga//interior.aspx?content_id=714899 Guilherme cedido ao Gil Vicente]\n* {{ForaDeJogo}}\n* {{90minut|26824}}\n\n{{Trabzonspor squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Guilherme Costa Marques}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Primeira Liga players]]\n[[Category:Ekstraklasa players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:S.C. Braga players]]\n[[Category:S.C. Braga B players]]\n[[Category:F.C. Vizela players]]\n[[Category:Gil Vicente F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Legia Warsaw players]]\n[[Category:Benevento Calcio players]]\n[[Category:Yeni Malatyaspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Trabzonspor footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Poland]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Italy]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate sport